description:
This 2017 Toyota Prius v Three is the perfect blend of efficiency, technology, and style. With its impressive 43 city/39 highway MPG, this Prius v delivers outstanding fuel economy without sacrificing performance or practicality.

Key features include:
Alloy Wheels
Back-up Camera
Bluetooth Connectivity
Cargo Cover
Cruise Control
Keyless Start
Navigation System

The Prius v's spacious interior and versatile cargo area make it an ideal choice for families or those with an active lifestyle. The advanced navigation system and Entune Premium Audio with App Suite provide seamless connectivity and entertainment on the go.

Slip behind the wheel and experience the smooth, responsive handling that makes the Prius v a joy to drive. The 1.8L 4-cylinder engine, paired with a continuously variable transmission, provides a refined and efficient driving experience.

Safety is a top priority, with features like anti-lock brakes, stability and traction control, and a suite of airbags to help protect you and your passengers. The Prius v's sleek, aerodynamic design not only looks great, but also contributes to its exceptional fuel efficiency.

Whether you're commuting, running errands, or embarking on a road trip, this 2017 Toyota Prius v Three is the perfect companion. Its combination of practicality, technology, and eco-friendly performance make it a standout in the compact hybrid segment.

We invite you to experience the Prius v's impressive capabilities for yourself. Visit our showroom and take this exceptional vehicle for a test drive. We're confident you'll be impressed by its versatility, efficiency, and value.

The Fazza Price shown includes a $1,000 trade-in assistance credit when you trade in an eligible vehicle (10 years old or newer with under 120,000 miles) and be in proper running condition at the time of the sale. If you do not have a qualifying trade-in, the purchase price will increase by $1,000. Taxes, title, registration, and an $895 documentation fee are not included. Contact Fazza Motors for the latest pricing and availability.

    Comfort
    • Heated steering wheel - A warm touch. Trying to drive with bulky winter gloves on isn't always easy. Keep your hands warm in cold temperatures so you can ditch the mitts and get a firm grip with this heated steering wheel.
    • Heated driver and front passenger seat cushions - That's hot. Heated driver and front passenger seat cushions provide more targeted warmth so you can get comfortable quicker in cold weather. If you have lower body pain, you might also be soothed by the heat while you drive. No matter the weather, find comfort in heated driver and front passenger seat cushions.
    Convenience
    • Keyfob engine start control - Get an early start. Remotely start your vehicle's engine from the key fob, ensuring your ride is ready to go when you get in. Now you can stay comfortable inside while your vehicle gets comfortable outside, thanks to Keyfob engine start control.
    Technology and Telematics
    • Voice activated integrated navigation system - A to B made easy! Whether it's an errand or a road trip, the voice activated integrated navigation system will guide you to your destination. No more bulky, impossible-to-fold maps, and no more stopping to ask for directions. Just tell it where you want to go, and the voice activated integrated navigation system shows you the right way.
    • Wireless connectivity - Strike the cord. Wireless technology makes it easy to place calls without having to fumble with your phone. It integrates your device with the system inside your vehicle for hands-free access. Keep connected and keep your hands on the wheel with wireless connectivity.

FACTORY CERTIFIED PRE-OWNED VEHICLE! NO HIDDEN FEES! ALL RECONDITIONING COSTS ARE FULLY INCLUDED IN OUR PRICES. SEE CPO DETAILS BELOW!

ONE OWNER!

ADVANCED PROTECH GROUP IV, PANORAMIC ROOF, NAVIGATION, HEADS UP DISPLAY, 20" WHEELS, 9 SPEAKER ALPINE PREMIUM SOUND SYSTEM, 10.1" TOUCHSCREEN DISPLAY AND SAFETY FEATURES!

Experience premium luxury, advanced safety, and powerful performance with the 2022 Jeep Grand Cherokee L Summit RWD in Bright White Clearcoat, equipped with a reliable 3.6L V6 24V VVT engine and smooth 8-speed automatic transmission. This sophisticated 3-row SUV features the Quick Order Package 22S and Advanced ProTech Group IV, delivering high-end upgrades like a Heads-Up Display, Interior Rear-Facing Camera, Night Vision with Pedestrian and Animal Detection, and a Rearview Auto-Dimming Digital Display Mirror. Stay protected with a full suite of driver-assist features including Adaptive Cruise Control with Stop & Go, Full-Speed Forward Collision Warning Plus, Active Lane Management, Blind Spot and Cross Path Detection, Intersection Collision Assist, Surround View Camera System, Park Assist with Stop, Pedestrian/Cyclist Emergency Braking, and Drowsy Driver Detection. Inside, enjoy first-class comfort with heated and ventilated front seats featuring 12-way power adjustments and back massagers, heated second-row bucket seats, and a power-folding third-row seat. Tech highlights include Uconnect 5 NAV with 10.1" touchscreen, Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, multi-color ambient LED lighting, and a 9-speaker amplified audio system with subwoofer. Additional luxuries include a heated steering wheel, four-zone automatic climate control, driver memory settings, remote start, and hands-free power liftgate. Riding on sleek 20" fully-painted aluminum silver wheels, the 2022 Jeep Grand Cherokee L Summit RWD blends rugged capability with refined elegance - making it the ultimate full-size SUV for families and adventurers alike.

description:
Discover the exceptional 2019 BMW X3 sDrive30i, a premium SUV that combines dynamic performance, sophisticated style, and unparalleled comfort. This meticulously maintained vehicle is a true testament to BMW's engineering excellence, offering a captivating driving experience that will exceed your expectations.

Boasting a striking white exterior, this X3 sDrive30i is equipped with a range of premium features that elevate the driving experience. Highlights include:

Convenience Package: Enjoy the convenience of LED headlights with cornering lights, keyless entry, lumbar support, panoramic moonroof, and SiriusXM satellite radio.
Navigation System: Stay connected with the advanced navigation system, featuring real-time traffic information and Apple CarPlay compatibility.
Heated Front Seats and Steering Wheel: Indulge in the comfort of heated seats and a heated steering wheel, ensuring a cozy ride in any weather.
Space-Saver Spare: Enjoy the peace of mind of having a space-saver spare tire, ready to handle unexpected situations.

Powered by a 2.0L I4 TwinPower Turbo engine, this BMW X3 delivers an exhilarating driving experience with 8-speed automatic transmission and rear-wheel drive. Boasting an impressive EPA-estimated 23 mpg in the city and 30 mpg on the highway, this SUV combines performance and efficiency for a truly rewarding ownership experience.

Beyond its exceptional performance, the 2019 X3 sDrive30i offers a refined and sophisticated interior, with features such as dual-zone automatic climate control, a premium sound system, and a sleek, modern design that complements the dynamic exterior. The spacious and versatile cabin provides ample room for passengers and cargo, making it the perfect companion for your daily commute or weekend adventures.

As a trusted BMW dealer, we take pride in offering our customers exceptional vehicles that exemplify the brand's commitment to quality and innovation. This 2019 X3 sDrive30i is a prime example of that dedication, and we believe it could be the perfect fit for your lifestyle.

We invite you to experience the exceptional 2019 BMW X3 sDrive30i for yourself. Schedule a test drive today and discover the joy of owning a truly remarkable SUV. We look forward to the opportunity to assist you in finding the perfect vehicle to meet your needs and exceed your expectations.

Elevate your driving experience with the exceptional 2025 Honda Civic Sport. This dynamic vehicle combines style, performance, and cutting-edge technology, making it the perfect choice for the discerning driver.

Boasting a striking black exterior, the Civic Sport commands attention on the road. Its sleek and aerodynamic design not only turns heads but also contributes to an impressive fuel efficiency of 31 city/39 highway MPG. Under the hood, the 2.0L I4 DOHC 16V engine and CVT transmission deliver a responsive and smooth driving experience, ensuring you'll enjoy every mile.

Key features include:
Alloy Wheels
Back-up Cam
Blind Spot Monitor
Bluetooth
Cruise Control
Keyless Start
Lane Departure Warning

The Civic Sport's advanced safety suite, including features like Adaptive Cruise Control, Blind Spot Information System, and a Rear-View Camera, provide you and your passengers with peace of mind on the road. Connectivity is seamless with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration, keeping you connected and entertained.

Step inside the Civic Sport, and you'll be greeted by a spacious and well-appointed cabin. The Cloth/Leatherette Seating Surfaces offer both comfort and style, while the Leather-Wrapped Steering Wheel and Shift Knob add a touch of refinement. The Split Folding Rear Seat provides versatility, allowing you to adapt the interior to your needs.

This exceptional Civic Sport is now available at Fazza Motors for just $25,699. With its impressive blend of performance, technology, and style, this Honda is sure to exceed your expectations. Visit our showroom today and experience the difference for yourself.

description:
**GOLD CERTIFIED** Thank you for choosing Butler Toyota, this Ruby Flare Pearl 2023 Toyota Sienna XLE is a great choice! Check out the following: One Owner! City 36/Hwy 36 RUBY FLARE PEARL Safety and Security
  • Lane departure prevention - Keep it between the lines. It only takes a moment of inattention for your vehicle to drift. With lane departure prevention, your vehicle takes corrective action to help you avoid unintentionally moving out of your lane. Lane departure prevention is an extra level of safety for you and those around you.
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
Our certification process keeps you in mind every step of the way. The TCUV standards apply from the time a Toyota dealer acquires the vehicle through to the final sale. Each candidate for certification can be a current model year vehicle, up to and including 10-year-old models, with 120,000 miles or less on the odometer. Prior to the rigorous 160-point inspection, every certified Toyota goes through a CARFAX vehicle history report is reviewed to ensure that only the best of the best vehicles receive the Toyota Certified Seal of approval. Our industry-leading heritage also comes with exceptional coverage policies. Our TCUV Gold and Silver benefits allow you to drive with confidence! With TCUV Gold, you get a 12-month/12,000-mile Limited Comprehensive Warranty1 a 7-year/100,000-mile Limited Powertrain Warranty2 plus 24-Hour Roadside Assistance for 7 years/100,000 miles3, honored at more than 1,400 Toyota dealers in the U.S. and Canada and More!

The Honda Accord has long been renowned for its exceptional quality, reliability, and value, and this 2023 Hybrid Sport model continues that tradition. Boasting a spacious and well-appointed interior, the Accord Hybrid Sport provides ample room for you and your passengers to enjoy the journey, whether commuting to work or embarking on a weekend adventure.

Beneath the sleek exterior lies a powertrain that seamlessly blends electric and gasoline power, delivering impressive acceleration and a smooth, responsive ride. The Accord Hybrid Sport's advanced safety features, including the Honda Sensing suite, provide added peace of mind, helping to keep you and your loved ones protected on the road.

We understand that purchasing a vehicle is a significant investment, and we're committed to ensuring you have a positive and stress-free experience. Our knowledgeable sales team is here to answer any questions you may have and guide you through the entire process, from test drive to final delivery.

Why Choose the 2016 Scion iA Sedan 4D?

Whether you're commuting to work, running errands, or heading out on a road trip, the Scion iA is ready to impress at every turn.


Stylish Design and Compact Convenience

Fuel-Efficient Performance with the 2016 Scion iA

This combination delivers an impressive balance of power and fuel efficiency, making it an ideal choice for budget-conscious drivers. With front-wheel drive (FWD) and advanced traction control, you can count on a stable and confident ride, whether you're cruising down the highway or navigating winding roads.


Advanced Safety Features for Peace of Mind
Safety is a top priority in the 2016 Scion iA, and it comes equipped with an array of features to keep you and your passengers protected. The sedan includes ABS (4-wheel) for reliable braking performance, stability control to help maintain traction in challenging conditions, and a suite of airbags, including dual front airbags, side airbags, and front and rear head curtain airbags. The backup camera provides added convenience and safety when reversing, making parking and maneuvering easier than ever.


Comfort and Convenience at Your Fingertips

The sedan is equipped with power windows and power door locks for effortless operation, while the tilt and telescoping steering wheel allows you to customize your driving position for maximum comfort. With the backup camera, you can park and reverse with confidence, knowing you have a clear view of your surroundings. The combination of advanced tech features makes every drive more enjoyable and stress-free.


Perfect for Daily Commutes and Long Drives
Whether you're navigating the busy streets of Santa Ana or embarking on a weekend getaway, the 2016 Scion iA is up for the task. Its electric power steering ensures a responsive and smooth driving experience, while cruise control helps you maintain a steady speed on long highway stretches. The sedan's compact size and excellent fuel economy make it a practical choice for both city driving and longer journeys.

description:
At Hartsville Chrysler Dodge Jeep Ram Fiat, we provide a trusted destination for quality vehicles and expert automotive care in the heart of Hartsville, South Carolina. Whether you're shopping for a hardworking truck, a family SUV, or a performance-driven ride, our team is here to help you drive home with confidence.

Highlights of this 2023 Ford F-150 XLT include:
Trailer Tow Package
Steering wheel mounted audio controls
Exterior Parking Camera Rear
Fully automatic headlights
Heated door mirrors
Power door mirrors
Class IV Trailer Hitch Receiver
Integrated Trailer Brake Controller
Pro Trailer Backup Assist & Pro Trailer Hitch Assist

This powerful F-150 is equipped with a 5.0L V8 engine and 10-speed automatic transmission, delivering impressive performance and capability. With 4-wheel drive, you'll have the confidence to tackle any terrain, whether hauling a heavy load or venturing off the beaten path. Fuel efficiency is also impressive, with an EPA-estimated 19 mpg in the city and 22 mpg on the highway.

The XLT trim level offers a wealth of premium features, including a SYNC 4 infotainment system with enhanced voice recognition, power windows, remote keyless entry, and a host of advanced safety technologies like ABS brakes, electronic stability control, and an emergency communication system. The spacious cabin and split-folding rear seat provide ample room for passengers and cargo, making this F-150 an excellent choice for work or play.

Backed by Ford's renowned reputation for durability and reliability, this 2023 F-150 XLT is ready to take on any challenge. With its impressive capabilities, advanced technology, and comfortable accommodations, it's the perfect companion for your next adventure.

Don't miss out on this opportunity to own a top-of-the-line Ford F-150. Schedule a test drive today and experience the power and versatility of this remarkable truck for yourself.

Serving Hartsville, Florence, Darlington, and the entire Pee Dee region, Hartsville Chrysler Dodge Jeep Ram Fiat offers one of South Carolina's best selections of new and used vehicles. Our dealership is dedicated to providing reliable service, competitive pricing, and a customer-focused experience from start to finish.

Our Certified, Accident Free, One Owner 2024 Ford F-150 STX SuperCrew 4X4 is tough, smart, and stylish in Carbonized Gray Metallic! Motivated by a Twin-TurboCharged 2.7 Liter EcoBoost V6 supplying 300hp to a 10 Speed Automatic transmission with selectable performance modes. Riding on a robust suspension for additional capability, this Four Wheel Drive truck also sees nearly 25mpg on the highway. Muscular and made for getting things done, our Ford's design shows off LED lighting, fog lamps, alloy wheels, running boards, a drop-in bedliner, heated power mirrors, skid plates, and a Class IV trailer hitch.

Rewarding features are at your service in our STX cabin, where you'll find comfortable cloth seats with power lumbar adjustability up front, a tilt/telescoping steering wheel, air conditioning, power accessories, cruise control, a 12V power outlet, and an eye-catching dashboard with both a 12-inch driver display and a 12-inch touchscreen. They support voice control, connected navigation, WiFi compatibility, Android Auto, Apple CarPlay, Bluetooth, and an AM/FM stereo for keeping in touch on the go.

Advanced Ford safety technologies can inspire confidence with automatic emergency braking, forward collision warning, lane-keeping assistance, a rearview camera, dynamic hitch assistance, hill-start assistance, rear parking sensors, Safety Canopy airbags, and more. With all that, the possibilities are practically endless in our F-150 STX! Save this Page and Call for Availability. We Know You Will Enjoy Your Test Drive Towards Ownership! Corwin Ford Nampa! Discover the ultimate in power, capability, and comfort with the 2024 Chevrolet Silverado 3500HD LT. This exceptional heavy-duty truck is built to handle the toughest jobs with ease, thanks to its impressive Duramax 6.6L V8 Turbodiesel engine that delivers an astonishing 470 horsepower and an incredible 975 lb-ft of torque.

3 Month/4,000 Mile Comprehensive Warranty
Gooseneck/5th Wheel Prep Package
Preferred Equipment Group 1LT
Suspension Package
SiriusXM w/360L
Steering Wheel Audio Controls
Air Conditioning
Bluetooth For Phone

220 Amp Alternator
Chevytec Spray-On Black Bedliner

OnStar & Chevrolet Connected Services Capable

This Silverado 3500HD LT is equipped with a host of premium features that elevate the driving experience. The Gooseneck/5th Wheel Prep Package allows you to tow with confidence, while the Preferred Equipment Group 1LT and Suspension Package provide exceptional ride quality and handling. Inside, you'll enjoy the convenience of SiriusXM with 360L, Steering Wheel Audio Controls, and Bluetooth connectivity, as well as the comfort of air conditioning and power-adjustable windows.

Certified by Ford Blue Advantage, this Silverado 3500HD LT has undergone a rigorous 127-point inspection to ensure it meets the highest standards of quality and reliability. With a comprehensive 3-month/4,000-mile warranty, you can drive with confidence, knowing that your investment is protected.

For better peace of mind, all our used vehicles have a 127-point inspection and come with a 5-day return, 30-day exchange (As-Is vehicles are excluded). Our exclusive Auto Rewards Program provides better value with Free First Oil change, Free Pa State Safety inspections, discounts for local merchants and more. Plus, you can earn up to $2000 towards your next vehicle just by servicing with Fred Beans! As Fred Beans always says, our used cars are better because our reputation depends on it.

Elevate your driving experience with this meticulously maintained 2026 Acura MDX Technology Package. This luxurious SUV is a true testament to Acura's commitment to exceptional engineering and uncompromising quality.

Navigation system: Google built-in (3-Years Unlimited Data Plan for In-Vehicle Apps)
Premium audio system: Acura/ELS Surround
19 Speakers
Premium Milano Leather Trimmed Seats
Power Liftgate
Heated Front Sport Seats
Blind Spot Information System
Rear Cross Traffic Monitor

Powered by a robust 3.5L V6 SOHC i-VTEC 24V engine mated to a smooth-shifting 10-Speed Automatic transmission, this MDX delivers a thrilling and efficient driving experience. With an impressive 19 city/26 highway MPG, you'll enjoy the perfect balance of performance and fuel economy.

The Technology Package elevates this MDX to new heights, offering a wealth of advanced features to enhance your daily commute and long-distance travels. From the cutting-edge navigation system with Google built-in to the premium Acura/ELS Surround audio system, every journey will be a true delight for the senses.

Indulge in the ultimate in comfort and convenience with features like heated front sport seats, a power liftgate, and a panoramic moonroof. Stay connected and informed with the Blind Spot Information System and Rear Cross Traffic Monitor, ensuring your safety and peace of mind on the road.

This Acura MDX Technology Package is backed by Acura's renowned Precision Certified program, offering unparalleled peace of mind. With a 182-point inspection, roadside assistance, and a comprehensive warranty, you can drive with confidence knowing your investment is protected.

description:
Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2021 GMC Sierra 1500 Denali. This powerful and versatile full-size pickup boasts a commanding presence on the road, combining rugged capability with refined luxury.

Highlighted features include:
White Frost Tricoat exterior
Driver Alert Package II with advanced safety technologies
Panoramic power sunroof

The Sierra 1500 Denali is built to impress, both inside and out. Its bold, distinctive styling commands attention, while the spacious and well-appointed cabin offers unparalleled comfort and convenience. Sink into the premium Forge perforated leather-appointed seats, which are both heated and ventilated for year-round comfort. The Bose premium audio system delivers an immersive listening experience, while wireless charging and multiple USB ports keep your devices powered and connected.

Under the hood, the EcoTec3 5.3L V8 engine delivers impressive power and efficiency, with 4-wheel drive capability to tackle any terrain. The 10-speed automatic transmission provides smooth, responsive shifting, and the Adaptive Ride Control suspension ensures a refined, composed ride.

Safety is a top priority in the Sierra 1500 Denali, with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies. The Driver Alert Package II includes features like Forward Collision Alert, Automatic Emergency Braking, Lane Keep Assist, and Adaptive Cruise Control, helping you navigate the road with confidence.

Whether you're hauling heavy loads, towing a trailer, or simply enjoying the daily commute, this 2021 GMC Sierra 1500 Denali is the ultimate expression of power, capability, and refined luxury. Experience the difference for yourself schedule a test drive today and discover the true potential of this exceptional full-size pickup.

This vehicle is being sold as Ingersoll Certified Pre-Owned. This program gives you piece of mind. You will receive. **A Vehicle Inspection and Reconditioning Form. **A Vehicle Carfax. **90 Days or 3000 miles of Powertrain Plus Limited Coverage **A Free Maintenance event including oil change and tire rotation within the first 12mo or 12,000 miles of driving (at an Ingersoll Automotive Location) This is not a manufacturer sponsored program.

Do not hesitate, call us now at 203.730.5766 to speak with our guest friendly product consultants to schedule your test drive.

Experience the exceptional 2024 Toyota Camry LE, a sophisticated and well-equipped sedan that combines style, comfort, and advanced technology. This captivating model offers a remarkable blend of performance, efficiency, and cutting-edge features, making it the perfect choice for the discerning driver.

Convenience Package
AM/FM radio: SiriusXM
Automatic temperature control
Front dual zone A/C
HomeLink
Power driver seat
Remote keyless entry
Steering wheel mounted audio controls
Emergency communication system: Safety Connect (1-year trial)
Smart Key System w/Push Button Start
Exterior Parking Camera Rear
Fully automatic headlights

Apple CarPlay/Android Auto

Powered by a 2.5L I4 DOHC 16V engine and an 8-Speed Automatic transmission, the Camry LE delivers an exceptional driving experience with impressive fuel efficiency, achieving an EPA-estimated 28 MPG in the city and 39 MPG on the highway. The sleek, silver exterior complements the well-appointed interior, creating a sophisticated and modern aesthetic that is sure to turn heads.

Step inside and discover the unparalleled comfort and convenience of the Camry LE. The spacious cabin offers ample room for both you and your passengers, while the premium fabric seating and front bucket seats provide exceptional support and luxury. The split-folding rear seat and generous cargo space ensure that you can easily accommodate all your needs, whether it's a weekend getaway or a daily commute.

The Camry LE is equipped with a wealth of advanced safety features, including a comprehensive suite of airbags, anti-lock brakes, electronic stability control, and a rearview camera, providing you with the peace of mind you deserve. Additionally, the Blind Spot Monitor with Rear Cross-Traffic Alert helps you navigate busy roads with confidence, while the Smart Key System with Push-Button Start adds a touch of modern convenience to your driving experience.

Discover the exceptional value and uncompromising quality of the 2024 Toyota Camry LE. This remarkable sedan is the perfect blend of style, performance, and technology, making it an exceptional choice for those seeking a sophisticated and well-equipped vehicle. Visit our showroom today and experience the Camry LE for yourself we're confident you'll be impressed.

description:
Introducing the 2024 Volkswagen Taos 1.5T SE, a compact SUV that combines sleek style, impressive performance, and a wealth of premium features to elevate your driving experience. With its turbocharged engine, smooth-shifting transmission, and efficient fuel economy, this Taos is the perfect companion for your daily commute and weekend adventures.




Slip behind the wheel and enjoy the Taos's spacious and well-appointed cabin, where you'll find a host of thoughtful amenities. The power driver's seat, dual-zone automatic climate control, and heated front seats ensure your comfort, while the 6-speaker audio system and SiriusXM radio keep you entertained. The Composition Media infotainment system with a 6.5-inch touchscreen puts a wealth of connectivity and information at your fingertips.

Safety is paramount in the Taos, with a suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies. The Active Blind Spot Monitor, 4-wheel disc brakes with ABS, and Electronic Stability Control work together to help keep you and your passengers secure on the road. And with the Exterior Parking Camera Rear, maneuvering in tight spaces is a breeze.

Beneath the sleek exterior lies a powertrain that delivers the perfect balance of power and efficiency. The turbocharged 1.5-liter engine, paired with an 8-speed automatic transmission, produces 158 horsepower and an impressive 36 mpg on the highway. Whether you're navigating city streets or tackling winding country roads, the Taos's responsive handling and smooth ride will have you eagerly anticipating every drive.

Experience the exceptional value and refined capabilities of the 2024 Volkswagen Taos 1.5T SE. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this impressive compact SUV can enhance your driving lifestyle. This clean one-owner 2023 Dodge Charger Scat Pack Widebody is pure American muscle with modern performance and technology to match. Powered by a legendary 6.4L SRT HEMI V8 delivering 485 horsepower, this Charger brings explosive acceleration, unmistakable sound, and widebody confidence in a head-turning B5 Blue finish. Backed by an 8-speed automatic transmission and performance-tuned suspension, it offers thrilling capability while still delivering everyday drivability and comfort.

Top Rated Features:

* 6.4L SRT HEMI V8 Engine with 485 Horsepower
* Scat Pack Widebody Package
* Adaptive Damping Suspension
* Brembo 6-Piston Front Brakes
* Active Exhaust System
* Line Lock and Launch Control
* Uconnect 4C with 8.4-Inch Touch Screen Display
* Apple CarPlay and Android Auto
* Heated and Ventilated Front Seats

If youre looking for a true performance sedan with aggressive styling, track-ready hardware, and everyday comfort, this Charger Scat Pack Widebody delivers in every category. A clean one-owner Carfax and iconic V8 power make this one a standout you wont want to miss.

Located ONLY at Sam Leman Chrysler Jeep in Bloomington! At the corner of Veterans and Commerce Parkway. Call today to set up a test drive at 1-309-662-5000.

Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2014 Acura MDX 3.5L Technology Package SH-AWD. This luxurious SUV is a true testament to Acura's commitment to performance, technology, and uncompromising quality.

Boasting a comprehensive suite of premium features, this MDX is tailored to exceed your expectations. Key highlights include:

Navigation System
10-Speaker Premium Audio System
Dual-Zone Automatic Climate Control
Heated and Ventilated Front Seats
Power Liftgate
Adaptive Suspension
Blind Spot Monitoring
Rear Cross-Traffic Alert

The MDX's powerful 3.5-liter V6 engine, paired with Acura's renowned Super Handling All-Wheel Drive (SH-AWD) system, delivers a thrilling and confident driving experience. With an EPA-estimated 27 highway MPG, this SUV strikes the perfect balance between performance and efficiency.

Stepping inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious and well-appointed cabin, crafted with the finest materials. The leather-trimmed interior, heated front seats, and power-adjustable driver's seat ensure exceptional comfort and support, whether you're navigating the daily commute or embarking on a weekend adventure.

The advanced technology features of the MDX further elevate your driving experience. The intuitive navigation system, coupled with the premium Acura/ELS Studio audio system, provides seamless connectivity and entertainment. The rear-view camera and various driver-assist technologies enhance safety and peace of mind, allowing you to navigate with confidence.

This 2014 Acura MDX 3.5L Technology Package SH-AWD is a true gem in the luxury SUV segment. With its exceptional performance, advanced features, and timeless design, it's the perfect vehicle to elevate your driving experience. Visit our showroom today to take this remarkable SUV for a test drive and discover why the MDX is the ultimate choice for discerning buyers.

Meticulously crafted with an array of premium features, this Silverado 3500HD High Country stands out from the crowd. Key highlights include:

Radiant Red Tintcoat exterior

Bose Premium 7-Speaker Sound System
Heated and ventilated front seats
Heated rear outboard seats
Wireless charging
Trailer Camera Provisions

Beneath its bold and distinctive exterior, this Silverado 3500HD High Country is engineered to deliver exceptional performance and capability. The powerful 6.6L V8 engine, paired with a smooth-shifting 10-speed automatic transmission, provides the perfect blend of power and efficiency to tackle any task with ease. Whether you're towing a heavy load or navigating rough terrain, this truck is designed to handle it all with confidence and control.

Step inside the cabin, and you'll be enveloped in a world of refined luxury. Heated and ventilated front seats, along with heated rear outboard seats, ensure maximum comfort in any weather. The Bose Premium 7-Speaker Sound System delivers an immersive audio experience, while the wireless charging pad keeps your devices powered up and ready to go.

For those who value connectivity and convenience, the Silverado 3500HD High Country delivers. The Bed View Camera with 2 Trailer Camera Provisions, along with the Ultrasonic Front & Rear Park Assist, make maneuvering and towing a breeze. The In-Vehicle Trailering App System provides seamless integration and control over your trailering needs.

This exceptional 2025 Chevrolet Silverado 3500HD High Country is more than just a truck it's a statement of power, sophistication, and uncompromising quality. The 2025 Ford F-150 XLT is a rugged and versatile pickup that's ready to take on any challenge. With its powerful 5.0L V8 engine, 4-wheel drive, and impressive towing and payload capabilities, this F-150 is built to handle the toughest jobs with ease.

Key features of this well-equipped model include:

5.0L V8 engine with Auto Start-Stop Technology
3.31 Axle Ratio and 7,100 lbs GVWR Payload Package
Chrome Door and Tailgate Handles, Wrapped Steering Wheel, and Chrome Single-Tip Exhaust
Dual-Zone Electronic Automatic Temperature Control
6" Angular Bright Anodized Step Bars
Black Painted Grille with Chrome Center Bar
SYNC 4 with Enhanced Voice Recognition
Rear Parking Sensors
Auto High-Beam Headlights

This F-150 XLT offers the perfect blend of capability, comfort, and convenience. With its spacious interior, advanced technology features, and rugged good looks, it's the ideal choice for work, play, or anything in between.

Whether you're hauling heavy loads, towing a trailer, or simply enjoying the open road, the 2025 Ford F-150 XLT has the power and versatility to get the job done. With its impressive fuel efficiency, delivering up to 22 mpg on the highway, this truck can go the distance without sacrificing performance.

At our dealership, we pride ourselves on offering a wide selection of high-quality vehicles to meet the diverse needs of our customers. The 2025 Ford F-150 XLT is a shining example of the exceptional craftsmanship and attention to detail that sets Ford apart.

We invite you to come in and experience the 2025 Ford F-150 XLT for yourself. Take it for a test drive and see how it can transform your driving experience. Our knowledgeable sales team is here to answer any questions you may have and help you find the perfect vehicle to suit your lifestyle and needs.

Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this impressive and versatile pickup. Visit our showroom today and let us help you drive away in the 2025 Ford F-150 XLT of your dreams.

description: At Schomp Honda, we go above and beyond to provide exceptional service not only for new car sales but also for our pre-owned vehicles. Our unique approach of One Price. One Person. One Hour. ensures a streamlined and transparent purchasing process for our used cars. Each vehicle in our pre-owned inventory undergoes rigorous inspections to meet our high standards of quality and reliability. Whether you're looking for a budget-friendly commuter car or a reliable family SUV, you can rely on Schomp Honda to offer a stress-free buying experience that respects your time and preferences. Visit us today, and let us assist you in finding the perfect used car that suits your lifestyle.We take pride in being recognized as a CarFax Top-Rated Dealer and DealerRater Dealer of the Year, showcasing our dedication to delivering exceptional customer service that has earned us these prestigious accolades. Our commitment to upholding outstanding service will continue for many years to come.This HONDA Odyssey Elite is a standout model in our pre-owned inventory. As a multipurpose passenger vehicle, this minivan is designed to meet diverse needs with its spacious interior and reliable performance. The vehicle is equipped with standard safety features such as ABS, Blind Spot Intervention, and Lane Keep System to ensure the well-being of you and your passengers.Under the hood, the HONDA Odyssey Elite is powered by a 3.5L V6 engine producing 280 horsepower. With a 10-speed automatic transmission and 4x2 drive type, this minivan offers a smooth and efficient driving experience. The exterior of the vehicle is finished in a sleek black color, adding a touch of sophistication to its overall design.Inside, the HONDA Odyssey Elite boasts a comfortable and feature-rich cabin. The front row is equipped with airbags for the driver and passenger, while side curtain airbags cover the 1st, 2nd, and 3rd rows for comprehensive protection. The interior offers seating for multiple passengers with manual seat belts for all occupants. The advanced entertainment system ensures an enjoyable ride for everyone on board.This pre-owned HONDA Odyssey Elite has an odometer reading of 19,515 miles, indicating its relatively low mileage. Additionally, the vehicle comes with a warranty for peace of mind regarding future maintenance and repairs.If you're in the market for a versatile and dependable minivan that excels in both safety and performance, the HONDA Odyssey Elite at Schomp Honda is the ideal choice. Contact us for more information or to schedule a test drive to experience this exceptional vehicle firsthand.

Vehicle Details
2025 Mazda CX-70 PHEV Premium Package Electrified Soul Meets Two-Row Sophistication
When did plug-in hybrids become this exhilarating? The 2025 Mazda CX-70 PHEV Premium Package answers with Hiroshima innovationa turbocharged 2.5-liter engine paired with electric motors unleashing 323 combined horsepower through intelligent all-wheel drive, 26 miles of pure electric range eliminating gas stations for daily commutes, Premium Plus package wrapping occupants in Nappa leather luxury, Bose premium audio transforming acoustics into concert experiences, and that Kodo "Soul of Motion" design philosophy proving electrification doesn't require sacrificing driving engagement. This isn't another compromised hybrid appliance or overpriced German complexity, it's Mazda's boldest statement proving two-row luxury meets electrified intelligencewhere 10-way power memory seats find your position automatically, panoramic moonroof bathes premium materials in natural light, 360-degree camera conquers tight spaces confidently, and that winged badge confirms you've discovered what happens when engineers obsessed with Jinba Ittai build their electrified flagship.

Critical Acclaim: The CX-70 represents Mazda's ambitious leap into electrified two-row luxury. Car and Driver praises "sports car dynamics meeting PHEV efficiency," while MotorTrend celebrates "the plug-in hybrid that actually rewards driving enthusiasts." Early owners rave: "electric torque transforms city driving," "interior rivals luxury Germans," and "Premium Package justifies every penny." This is validation from driving purists, sustainability-minded families, and professionals who discovered Mazda's PHEV delivers genuine performance without range anxiety or environmental guilt.

The exterior broadcasts sophisticated presencesignature wing grille commanding attention, LED headlights with adaptive lighting scripting Mazda's evolution, sculpted bodywork suggesting motion through Japanese landscapes, fastback roofline adding coupe-like elegance to SUV practicality, and 20-inch dark-finish alloy wheels balancing athleticism with refinement. The longer wheelbase versus CX-5 creates commanding stance and exceptional rear legroom. Machine Gray Metallic or Soul Red Crystal Metallic paint (additional cost, hand-applied by Takumi masters) showcases Japanese craftsmanship aging beautifullythis design transcends trends.

PHEV Powerhouse: The plug-in hybrid system demonstrates electrified excellence323 combined horsepower merging 2.5-liter turbocharged engine with electric motors, instant electric torque creating exhilarating acceleration from stops, 26 miles of EPA-estimated all-electric range (perfect for daily commutes eliminating gas consumption entirely), 17.8 kWh battery charging fully in approximately 3 hours on 240V, and seamless transitions between electric/hybrid modes you'll barely notice. Zero-to-60 happens in approximately 5.8 secondsseriously quick for electrified luxury. Combined fuel economy delivers approximately 56 MPGe when maximizing electric rangeimpressive for 4,400 pounds of premium SUV.

i-ACTIV AWD Intelligence: Mazda's predictive all-wheel drive monitors 27 parametersoutside temperature, wiper activity, throttle inputs, steering angle, road conditionsdistributing torque before you need it. Combined with G-Vectoring Control Plus (adjusting power delivery and braking through corners) and Kinematic Posture Control (using brake inputs to reduce body roll), the CX-70 delivers that horse-and-rider connection Mazda engineers obsess over. This isn't electrified transportation, it's electrified driving pleasure.

Premium Package Luxury: Enter and experience Japanese artistry elevatedNappa leather seating with contrast stitching throughout, heated and ventilated front seats conquering seasonal extremes, 10-way power driver's seat with memory, heated steering wheel wrapped in premium leather, genuine wood trim (not plastic imposters), brushed satin chrome accents, and ambient lighting creating sanctuary atmospheres. Build quality rivals luxury marqueesevery surface rewards touch, materials age gracefully, assembly tolerances satisfy perfectionists. That new-car aroma blends premium leather, natural wood, and Japanese attention to detail normally reserved for six-figure luxury.

Technology Harmony: The 12.3-inch center display integrates connectivity seamlesslywireless Apple CarPlay/Android Auto, wireless smartphone charging pad, voice recognition understanding naturally, and navigation guiding intelligently. The 12.3-inch digital driver display presents information clearly with customizable layouts. Head-up display projects essential data onto windshield keeping eyes forward. The Bose premium audio system (12 speakers including subwoofer) delivers impressive acousticsconcerts sound live, podcasts achieve NPR clarity, and perfectly tuned bass resonates without booming.

Two-Row Sanctuary: Rear passengers enjoy class-leading spaceadult-friendly legroom rivaling three-row competitors, supportive seating wrapped in premium materials, individual climate vents, heated outboard seats, and dedicated USB-C charging ports. The longer wheelbase creates lounge-like comfort previously impossible in two-row packaging. The 29.1 cubic-foot cargo area (56.3 with rear seats folded) accommodates weekend adventures, electric bike gear, or spontaneous antique discoveries. Power liftgate opens with foot-activated sensor.

i-ACTIVSENSE Safety: Standard technologies include radar cruise control with stop-and-go capability, lane departure warning with lane-keep assist, blind-spot monitoring with rear cross-traffic alert, smart brake support (automatic emergency braking), traffic sign recognition, and driver attention alert. The 360-degree camera with front/rear parking sensors provides bird's-eye confidence. Mazda's commitment to safety protects occupants obsessively while maintaining driving engagement.

Electrified Convenience: Charge port illumination aids nighttime charging, scheduled charging optimizes off-peak electricity rates, remote climate pre-conditioning uses wall power rather than battery charge, and multiple drive modes (Normal, Sport, EV) adapt personality instantly. Monitor charging status, battery range, and energy flow through smartphone app or dashboard displays.

If youre searching for a luxury SUV that perfectly blends high-performance capability, advanced technology, and refined comfort, this 2023 Acura MDX Type S Advance AWD is an exceptional choice. The Type S Advance trim takes the MDX to the next level with a turbocharged V6 engine, sport-tuned handling, and Super Handling All-Wheel Drive (SH-AWD) for precision driving in all conditions. Whether navigating suburban streets in Libertyville, Vernon Hills, Mundelein, or Lake Forest, or heading out on weekend adventures through Gurnee, Grayslake, or Waukegan, this MDX delivers both thrilling performance and composed luxury.

With seating for seven and flexible cargo space, its ideal for family trips, commuting, or longer drives to downtown Chicago or weekend escapes to Lake Geneva.

With its combination of low mileage, performance-oriented AWD, and Acuras reputation for luxury and reliability, this 2023 MDX Type S Advance is perfect for buyers in Buffalo Grove, Schaumburg, Palatine, Glenview, Deerfield, and Lincolnshire who want a sophisticated, capable SUV that excels in both city and suburban driving.

Elevate your driving experience with the 2023 Subaru Legacy Sport. This exceptional sedan offers a captivating blend of style, performance, and advanced technology, making it the perfect companion for your daily commute or weekend adventures.

Navigation System
Standard Model
6 Speakers
AM/FM radio: SiriusXM
Radio: Subaru STARLINK 11.6" Multimedia Nav System
Air Conditioning
Automatic temperature control
Front dual zone A/C
Rear window defroster
Power driver seat
Power steering
Power windows
Remote keyless entry
Steering wheel mounted audio controls

Powered by a 2.4L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V engine and Lineartronic CVT, the 2023 Subaru Legacy Sport delivers a smooth and efficient driving experience, with an impressive 23 MPG in the city and 31 MPG on the highway. The standard Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive system provides confident handling and exceptional traction, ensuring you can tackle any road with ease.

Step inside the spacious and well-appointed cabin, where you'll be surrounded by premium features designed to enhance your comfort and convenience. Enjoy the convenience of the Subaru STARLINK 11.6" Multimedia Navigation System, which seamlessly integrates your smartphone and provides turn-by-turn directions. The dual-zone automatic climate control and heated front seats will keep you comfortable, no matter the weather. And with the power moonroof, you can let in the natural light and enjoy the great outdoors.

Safety is a top priority in the 2023 Subaru Legacy Sport, with a host of advanced driver-assistance technologies to give you peace of mind on the road. Features like the Rear-View Camera, Blind-Spot Detection, and Automatic High-Beam Headlights work together to help you stay aware of your surroundings and react quickly to potential hazards.

Whether you're commuting to the office, taking a road trip, or simply enjoying the drive, the 2023 Subaru Legacy Sport is the perfect companion. Experience the perfect blend of style, performance, and technology by scheduling a test drive today. We're confident you'll be impressed by this exceptional sedan.

This vehicle is being sold as Ingersoll Certified Pre-Owned. This program gives you piece of mind. You will receive. **A Vehicle Inspection and Reconditioning Form. **A Vehicle Carfax. **90 Days or 3000 miles of Powertrain Plus Limited Coverage **A Free Maintenance event including oil change and tire rotation within the first 12mo or 12,000 miles of driving (at an Ingersoll Automotive Location). This vehicle is eligible to be upgraded to Ingersoll Certified Plus for $749. That will give you the additional benefits of 12mo or 12,000 miles of limited exclusionary coverage, 6 years or up to 100,000 miles of powertrain limited coverage (from original in-service date), courtesy transportation for covered repairs, and road side assistance. **A Vehicle Exchange Program if dissatisfied in the first 3 days or 150 miles of ownership. This is not a manufacturer sponsored program

Do not hesitate, call us now at 203.730.5766 to speak with our guest friendly product consultants to schedule your test drive.

Elevate your driving experience with the remarkable 2025 GMC Sierra 2500HD AT4. This powerhouse of a truck is engineered to conquer any terrain, delivering unparalleled capability and refined comfort.

Standout features include:
Gooseneck/5th Wheel Prep Package

Heated and Ventilated Front Seats

Wireless Charging
Trailer Cam Provisions & Trailer Viewing Software
HD Surround Vision

Forward Collision Alert
Front Pedestrian Braking

Beneath the sculpted exterior lies a 6.6L V8 engine mated to a 10-speed automatic transmission, providing the perfect balance of power and efficiency. The Sierra 2500HD AT4 is built to tackle the most demanding tasks, whether hauling heavy loads or venturing off the beaten path.

Comfort and convenience are paramount, with features like dual-zone climate control, a heated steering wheel, and a premium Bose sound system that will elevate your driving experience. The AT4's off-road-tuned suspension and advanced 4WD system ensure you can conquer any terrain with confidence.

Safety is also a top priority, with a suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies, including Automatic Emergency Braking, Forward Collision Alert, and Front Pedestrian Braking, keeping you and your passengers secure.

The 2025 GMC Sierra 2500HD AT4 is a true workhorse, blending exceptional capability, refined comfort, and cutting-edge technology. Experience the difference for yourself schedule a test drive today and discover the power and versatility that this remarkable truck has to offer.

description:
Elevate your driving experience with the exceptional 2023 BMW 5 Series 530e iPerformance. This sophisticated hybrid sedan combines dynamic performance, cutting-edge technology, and unparalleled luxury, making it the perfect choice for the discerning driver.

Boasting a striking Skyscraper Gray Metallic exterior, this 530e iPerformance is equipped with a host of premium features that will captivate you. Highlights include:

Power Tailgate
Head-Up Display
harman/kardon Surround Sound System
Heated Front Seats
Heated Steering Wheel

The Connected Package Pro and Premium Package further elevate your driving experience, offering seamless connectivity, advanced safety features, and unmatched comfort. Indulge in the 12-speaker harman/kardon sound system, enjoy the convenience of Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, and let the power moonroof flood your cabin with natural light.

Beneath the sleek exterior lies the heart of this remarkable vehicle a 2.0L 4-cylinder hybrid powertrain that delivers an exceptional blend of performance and efficiency. With the 8-speed Automatic Sport transmission and xDrive all-wheel drive, you'll enjoy confident handling and responsive acceleration, all while achieving impressive fuel economy.

The 530e iPerformance's interior is a true sanctuary of luxury and refinement. Sink into the power-adjustable, heated front seats, wrapped in premium Sensatec upholstery, and let the driver's seat memory function remember your preferred settings. The leather-wrapped steering wheel and genuine wood accents throughout the cabin create an atmosphere of sophistication and attention to detail.

Safety is of the utmost importance, and the 530e iPerformance delivers with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver assistance technologies. From the Rear View Camera to the Emergency Communication System, you can drive with confidence, knowing you and your passengers are well-protected.

Experience the pinnacle of luxury, performance, and technology with the 2023 BMW 5 Series 530e iPerformance. We invite you to visit our showroom and take this exceptional vehicle for a test drive. Prepare to be captivated by its unrivaled blend of style, power, and innovation.

description:
The 2024 Nissan Pathfinder SL is a versatile and well-equipped SUV that's ready to elevate your driving experience. With its sleek exterior, spacious interior, and impressive performance, this Pathfinder is the perfect companion for your adventures.

Boasting a striking white exterior, this Pathfinder SL comes equipped with a range of premium features that set it apart. Highlights include:


Under the hood, this Pathfinder is powered by a robust 3.5L V6 DOHC engine, paired with a smooth-shifting 9-speed automatic transmission and capable 4WD system. With an EPA-estimated 21 mpg in the city and 27 mpg on the highway, you'll enjoy exceptional efficiency and the freedom to explore.

Step inside the Pathfinder SL, and you'll be greeted by a spacious and well-appointed cabin. The leather-appointed seating surfaces provide both comfort and style, while the heated front seats and steering wheel ensure you stay cozy, even on the coldest days. The NissanConnect system with Navigation and Services keeps you connected and in control, seamlessly integrating with your smartphone's Apple CarPlay and Android Auto.

Safety is a top priority in the Pathfinder SL, with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies. From the Rear Parking Camera to the Blind Spot Warning and Intelligent Forward Collision Warning, you can navigate with confidence, knowing you and your loved ones are well-protected.

Whether you're embarking on a family road trip, tackling off-road adventures, or simply commuting in style, the 2024 Nissan Pathfinder SL is ready to rise to the occasion. With its impressive capabilities, refined interior, and cutting-edge features, this SUV is a compelling choice that's sure to exceed your expectations.

We invite you to visit our showroom and experience the 2024 Nissan Pathfinder SL for yourself. Take it for a test drive and discover how this exceptional SUV can enhance your driving experience. We're confident you'll be impressed by its versatility, performance, and exceptional value. We look forward to welcoming you and helping you find the perfect Pathfinder to suit your lifestyle.

description: This Sedan was driven 12,962 miles/year which is less than the industry average, on top of that the automatic transmission provides for a smooth yet reliable ride. This smooth 6 Cylinder engine is ideal for performance and fuel economy, on top of that the AWD system increases traction - particularly in snow and rain and improves handling on dry surfaces. You'll never fear a blind spot again when backing up thanks to the Infiniti back-up camera option whereas push-button keyless start couldn't be simpler, just slide behind the wheel, with the key fob in your pocket, briefcase or purse. The power roof lets you enjoy sun or moon light at the push of a button at the same time the factory built in HD radio gives you more music, talk shows and news without any monthly subscription fees. The satellite radio delivers a variety of stations that's sure to make any road trip more exciting, furthermore the Bluetooth connection is the ultimate option for hands-free calling while driving. The MP3 player enables you to listen to hours of uninterrupted music, furthermore the premium sound system lets you enjoy every note of your favorite album. Listening to music from any device with the built-in AUX input makes any road trip exciting, not to mention the keyless entry option adds to the convenience of owning this vehicle. The installed stability control improves traction on slippery or icy roads, moreover the cruise control takes much of the foot-work out of long distance driving. The alarm system keeps your vehicle safe and saves you money on insurance, meanwhile the heated front seats warm up before the air in the passenger compartment is fully warmed by the heater which is a big plus for cold days. The brake assist delivers a huge safety advantage - if the system identifies an emergency, it automatically initiates full braking faster than any driver can move their foot while the tire pressure monitoring system keeps an eye on tire inflation continually, for maximum safety in everyday driving situations. The driver lumbar support is most appreciated after a long road trip, whats more is the Dual-Shift transmission provides for a sport inspired driving experience. The power windows are so convenient that it's hard to make do without them, meanwhile the installed CD player lets you Enjoy your favorite CD's on the go. The traction control helps to provide more protection in dangerous weather, in addition to the steering wheel audio controls are a great safety feature which keep your hands and eyes on the road.

description: Discover the 2024 Ford F-250SD, a robust pickup truck built for both work and adventure. With only 11,181 miles on the odometer, this used model boasts a striking Oxford White exterior complemented by a Medium Dark Slate interior, offering a sleek yet practical aesthetic. Powered by a 6.8-liter V8 engine with 405 horsepower and 445 lb-ft of torque, it delivers impressive performance and towing capacity. The 10-speed automatic transmission and 4WD drivetrain ensure smooth handling and superior stability across challenging terrains. This Ford F-250SD is designed to meet the demands of heavy-duty tasks while providing modern convenience features like Apple CarPlay, a backup camera, Bluetooth connectivity, a tow package, and a Wi-Fi hotspot, making every drive safer and more connected. This versatile pickup seats six comfortably and features four doors for easy access. Its standard gray interior provides a durable and comfortable environment for work or leisure. The naturally aspirated engine offers reliable power, and the vehicles spacious design makes it ideal for hauling, towing, or daily commuting. With its combination of raw capability and smart tech features, the 2024 Ford F-250SD is a compelling choice for those seeking a used truck that balances performance, comfort, and connectivity. 2024 Ford F-250SD Safety and Security Features Safety is a priority in the 2024 Ford F-250SD, equipped with essential features such as four-wheel anti-lock braking system (ABS) to enhance stopping power and stability under heavy loads. Additionally, it includes a programmable safety key that allows owners to set driving parameters, providing an extra layer of security and control over vehicle usage. 2024 Ford F-250SD Entertainment and Technology Features The Ford F-250SD is packed with advanced entertainment and technology features, including FordPass Connect compatibility that allows smart device app integration for remote vehicle management. Hands-free phone call capabilities and voice-activated radio ensure seamless communication and entertainment, while the 8-inch touch screen display offers intuitive control over infotainment options. Other features include app marketplace integration, engine start via smart device app, electronic messaging assistance with read and voice-operated functions, and a USB auxiliary audio input, making every journey more connected and enjoyable. 2024 Ford F-250SD Performance Features The 2024 Ford F-250SDs performance is anchored by its electronic high-low 4WD selector, providing drivers with optimal traction and control in varying conditions. Its part-time 4WD system allows for versatile drive modes, making it well-suited for off-road adventures or heavy-duty hauling, ensuring the trucks capability matches the demands of any task. description:
Discover the ultimate driving experience with this exceptional 2020 Nissan Murano Platinum. Boasting a stunning white exterior and a meticulously maintained interior, this one-owner Murano is a true gem that will exceed your expectations.

Packed with an impressive array of features, this Murano Platinum stands out from the crowd. Enjoy the convenience of cutting-edge technology, including:
Navigation system with NissanConnect
Apple CarPlay and Android Auto
Blind spot warning
Rear backup camera
Panoramic sunroof
Hands-free Bluetooth connectivity

The Murano's 3.5L V6 DOHC engine, paired with Nissan's renowned Xtronic CVT transmission and all-wheel drive, delivers a smooth and responsive driving experience. With an impressive 20 MPG in the city and 28 MPG on the highway, this Murano offers exceptional fuel efficiency, making it the perfect companion for your daily commute or weekend adventures.

Step inside the luxurious cabin and experience the ultimate in comfort and style. The Murano Platinum features premium leather-appointed seating, heated and ventilated front seats, and a heated steering wheel, ensuring you and your passengers stay cozy and relaxed no matter the weather. The spacious cargo area, complete with a retractable cover and cargo net, provides ample room for all your belongings.

Safety is a top priority in the Murano Platinum, with features like blind spot warning, rear cross-traffic alert, and a comprehensive suite of airbags to give you peace of mind on the road. The Nissan brand is known for its commitment to quality and reliability, and this Murano is no exception.

As a family-owned dealership serving the Sarasota community for over 30 years, we take pride in offering a personalized and hassle-free buying experience. Our team of knowledgeable professionals is dedicated to ensuring your complete satisfaction, from the moment you step onto our lot to long after you drive off in your new Murano Platinum.

Don't miss your chance to own this exceptional 2020 Nissan Murano Platinum. Contact us today to schedule a test drive and experience the ultimate in style, comfort, and performance.

description:
Discover the exceptional 2020 Jeep Cherokee Limited, a vehicle that seamlessly blends rugged capability with refined sophistication. This stunning SUV is the perfect companion for your adventurous lifestyle, offering the perfect balance of power, technology, and style.

Packed with premium features, the 2020 Jeep Cherokee Limited stands out from the crowd. Highlights include a Quick Order Package 26P High Altitude, Trailer Tow Group, and a Power Front/Fixed Rear Full Sunroof, providing unparalleled convenience and versatility. The Granite Crystal Exterior Accents and Anodized Gun Metal Interior Accents add a touch of elegance, while the 8.4" Touchscreen Display with Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, and Uconnect 4C Nav keeps you connected and entertained.

This 2020 Jeep Cherokee Limited is powered by a robust 3.2L V6 engine paired with a 9-Speed 948TE Automatic transmission, delivering an impressive 19 city/27 highway MPG. The 4WD system ensures confident handling in any terrain, while the class-leading towing capacity of the Trailer Tow Group makes it easy to bring your toys along for the ride.

Step inside and you'll be greeted by Premium Leather Trimmed Bucket Seats, a Heated Steering Wheel, and Heated Front Seats, creating a sanctuary of comfort and luxury. The Dual-Zone Automatic Temperature Control and Rear Window Defroster keep you and your passengers comfortable, no matter the weather.

Safety is paramount in the 2020 Jeep Cherokee Limited, with features like Blind Spot Monitoring, Rear Cross-Path Detection, and a ParkView Rear Back-Up Camera providing added peace of mind. The advanced airbag system and Electronic Stability Control further enhance your protection on the road.

Whether you're embarking on a family adventure, navigating the daily commute, or exploring the great outdoors, the 2020 Jeep Cherokee Limited is the perfect companion. Experience the perfect blend of capability, technology, and style by scheduling a test drive today.

description: Take on your next adventure with this versatile Cactus Gray 2021 Ford Ranger Lariat. This midsize truck is the perfect choice for someone who wants the power of a pickup without the massive size of a full-size vehicle. As a one-owner vehicle with a clean history and no damage, it has been exceptionally well-maintained. It comes complete with all your essential records, books, and keys, so you can start your journey with total confidence.Under the hood, you will find a peppy 2.3L EcoBoost engine that provides plenty of muscle for both city driving and highway cruising. This Ranger is equipped with the FX2 Package, which adds off-road tuned suspension and an electronic-locking rear differential for better traction. Whether you are heading to a weekend campsite or just navigating daily traffic in Clearwater, the smooth 10-speed automatic transmission makes every drive feel effortless.The Lariat trim ensures you don't have to sacrifice comfort for capability. The cabin is loaded with premium features like leather-trimmed seating and the SYNC 3 infotainment system, which makes it easy to stay connected. You will also enjoy the convenience of a built-in navigation system and the SecuriCode keyless-entry keypad. With dual-zone automatic climate control and a leather-wrapped steering wheel, the interior feels more like a luxury SUV than a rugged work truck.Safety and technology are front and center in this model. The included Technology Package features Adaptive Cruise Control and a Forward Sensing System to help you stay aware of your surroundings. Parking and hitching up are simple thanks to the exterior parking camera and the Trailer Tow Package, which includes a Class IV trailer hitch receiver. Whether you are towing a small boat or a utility trailer, this Ranger is ready to get the job done right.At INFINITI of Clearwater, we are excited to show you why this Cactus Gray Ranger is such a standout pick. It combines Fords legendary toughness with modern features that make it a joy to drive every day. Come visit us to see this one-owner truck in person and take it for a spin. Our team is ready to provide a straightforward and professional experience to help you get on the road in a vehicle you love.INFINITI of Clearwater's pre-owned department believes in upfront, transparent, internet based pricing. Unlike our competitors, we don't have adds for reconditioning, tint (that many times was already installed), all weather mats, pin stripes, the list can go on and on! No adds, just simple, transparent, low prices! Call 727-275-8456 for more details!

2022 Lexus RX 350 Luxury Reliability Only 38,472 Miles

Experience refined comfort, premium craftsmanship, and Lexus reliability in this 2022 Lexus RX 350, one of the most trusted and best-selling luxury SUVs on the market. With only 38,472 miles, this RX 350 delivers smooth performance, excellent ride quality, and a long list of modern features designed to elevate every drive.

Powered by Lexus proven 3.5L V6 engine paired with an 8-speed automatic transmission, the RX 350 offers quiet acceleration, a refined driving feel, and outstanding long-term dependability. Whether you're commuting or traveling with family, this luxury SUV provides the perfect balance of power, comfort, and efficiency. The cabin is meticulously crafted with premium materials, intuitive controls, and a spacious layout that ensures comfort for both driver and passengers.

Inside, you'll enjoy Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, touchscreen infotainment, premium audio, Bluetooth, and a backup camera. Lexus Safety System+ enhances confidence with advanced features including Pre-Collision Warning, Lane Keeping Assist, Adaptive Cruise Control, and Road Sign Assist, making this RX 350 a smart and safe choice for everyday driving. Dual-zone climate control, push-button start, and a power liftgate add everyday convenience.
The stylish exterior features LED headlights, alloy wheels, sleek body lines, and the signature Lexus spindle grille, giving the RX 350 a bold and upscale presence on the road. Designed for comfort, capability, and reliability, this luxury SUV stands out as an excellent option for drivers seeking long-lasting value and a premium driving experience.

Key Features:
3.5L V6 engine
8-speed automatic transmission
Apple CarPlay & Android Auto
Touchscreen infotainment
Lexus Safety System+
Backup camera
LED headlights
Alloy wheels
Power liftgate

Cornering brake control enhances stability during turns, reducing the risk of skidding, while the electronic parking brake with auto-off function simplifies parking and prevents accidental rollaways. These features work together to provide a comprehensive safety net, giving you peace of mind whether on the job or during daily commutes. 2022 Ford F-150 Entertainment and Technology Features The 2022 F-150 is packed with advanced entertainment and connectivity options, starting with FordPass Connect that allows compatibility with smart device apps, including remote engine start for added convenience. The touchscreen display serves as the central hub for radio and in-car app marketplace integration, providing access to a wide range of digital services. Experience efficiency and premium comfort in this 2022 Hyundai Kona Electric Limited FWD, finished in sleek Ultra Black and powered by a responsive all-electric motor for zero-emissions driving. This well-equipped compact electric SUV features a 10.25-inch touchscreen display with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, built-in navigation, and a premium harman/kardon sound system for an elevated driving experience. Enjoy year-round comfort with heated and ventilated front seats, a heated leather steering wheel, leather seat trim, and a power moonroof that adds an open-air feel. ** INBOUND UNIT -- CARFAX CERTIFIED 1 OWNER, ACCIDENT FREE, GREAT SERVICE HISTORYY ... RARE ** Why BUY from Bill Jacobs Volkswagen? When you choose this Nautical Blue Metallic 2022 Mercedes-Benz E-Class E 450 with 72,963 miles, you are not just buying a used vehicle - you are investing in quality, reliability and peace of mind. Our clientele depend on us for Transparent Pricing, Convenience and, most importantly, Customer FIRST Service! No Accidents! One Owner! What this vehicle includes: Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.
Come on in to Bill Jacobs Volkswagen today at 2211 Aurora Ave Naperville IL 60540 or call 844-746-7928 to schedule a test drive!

Discover the perfect blend of power, capability, and refined luxury in this 2020 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 LTZ. This exceptional truck is a true masterpiece, engineered to exceed your expectations and elevate your driving experience.

Boasting a stunning Blue exterior, this Silverado 1500 LTZ is equipped with a robust EcoTec3 5.3L V8 engine, delivering an impressive 17 city/24 highway MPG. But this vehicle is more than just raw power it's a testament to Chevrolet's commitment to innovation and craftsmanship.

Key features include:
LTZ PLUS PACKAGE
LTZ CONVENIENCE PACKAGE II
Wheels: 20" x 9" Polished Finish
Tires: 275/60R20SL All-Terrain, Blackwall
Bose Premium Audio System
Wireless Charging
Chevrolet Infotainment 3 Premium System with Navigation
Heated Steering Wheel
Ventilated Front Seats
Integrated Trailer Brake Controller
Hitch Guidance with Hitch View

Step inside and you'll be enveloped in a world of unparalleled comfort and convenience. The premium leather-appointed seating, heated and ventilated front seats, and heated rear outboard seats provide a level of luxury that will leave you feeling truly pampered. The Bose premium audio system and Chevrolet Infotainment 3 Premium System with Navigation ensure you're always connected and entertained.

But the Silverado 1500 LTZ isn't just about creature comforts it's also a workhorse built to handle your toughest tasks. With the available LTZ Plus Package, you'll enjoy features like the 120-volt bed-mounted power outlet, the EZ Lift power lock and release tailgate, and the advanced trailering system, making it easier than ever to tackle any job or adventure.

Whether you're hauling heavy loads, towing your boat or trailer, or simply enjoying the open road, this 2020 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 LTZ is the perfect companion. Experience the perfect blend of power, capability, and refined luxury schedule a test drive today and discover why this truck is the ultimate choice for discerning drivers like you.

description:
2025 Subaru Outback Premium AWD - Certified Pre-Owned - 26/32 MPG - heated seats, keyless start & power liftgate, Android Auto/Apple CarPlay.

AWD | 2.5L H-4 | CVT | 26/32 MPG | Heated front seats | Keyless access w/push-button start | Power liftgate | Android Auto & Apple CarPlay | Wi-Fi hotspot | Back-up camera | Blind-Spot Monitor & Rear Cross-Traffic Alert | Adaptive cruise control | Lane keep assist | LED headlights w/auto high beams | Heated mirrors w/turn signals | Multi-zone climate control | Aluminum wheels | Autumn Green Metallic

CPO benefits

152-point inspection | 84 mo/100,000 mi powertrain from original in-service date | $0 deductible | Roadside assistance | Vehicle history | Transferable warranty | SiriusXM 3-month trial | STARLINK 1-year trial.

Performance

Subaru Symmetrical AWD teams with the 2.5L H-4 and CVT for surefooted traction in rain and snow and smooth, efficient cruising.
26/32 MPG helps keep road-trip and commute costs in check.

Comfort & Convenience

Heated front seats and a leather steering wheel add cold-weather comfort, while keyless access, push-button start, and a power liftgate simplify loading and go.
8-way power driver seat w/lumbar, rear bench pass-through, cargo shade, and three 12V outlets support busy days.

Technology

Android Auto and Apple CarPlay integrate maps, playlists, and calls, the Wi-Fi hotspot keeps passengers connected.
Back-up camera, trip computer, telematics, turn-by-turn nav directions, universal garage door opener, and two front LCDs add everyday ease.

Safety

Driver aids include adaptive cruise control, lane keep assist, lane departure warning, front collision mitigation, driver monitoring, and stability/traction control.
Blind-Spot Monitor with Rear Cross-Traffic Alert, tire-pressure monitoring, child safety locks, and airbags with knee protection further enhance confidence.

Exterior & Interior

LED headlights with auto-leveling and automatic high beams, fog lamps, heated mirrors with turn signals, rear spoiler, privacy glass, luggage rack, and aluminum wheels project capability.
Slate Black cloth with heated front buckets, power driver seat, leather steering wheel, air filtration, seatback storage, and concealed cargo area storage keep the cabin smart and comfortable.

Driving Experience

Quiet, composed ride with secure AWD grip and relaxed steering.

History Summary

Certified Pre-Owned by Subaru.
Clean History Report - no accidents or damage reported to CARFAX.
No Open Recalls at this time.
Active factory warranty remaining.

This Subaru Outback Touring's low mileage means years of reliable driving ahead, and its fuel-efficient 2.5L engine balances power with economy for daily driving and longer trips.
