This 2020 Subaru Outback Touring is the kind of vehicle that makes everyday driving feel just a little more refined. As the top-of-the-line Outback, it delivers a perfect balance of comfort, capability, and confidence, wrapped in Subarus legendary all-wheel-drive performance. It has just had a recent 60k service completed and features brand-new rear brakes, so its been properly cared for and is ready for many more miles ahead.

The Touring trim brings a premium feel throughout the cabin, with upscale materials, a quiet ride, and thoughtful details designed to make long drives and daily commutes equally enjoyable. Whether youre navigating city streets, cruising the highway, or heading out for a weekend adventure, the Outback's smooth ride, excellent visibility, and sure-footed handling make it a pleasure to drive in all conditions.

This Outback Touring is a great choice for someone looking for a well-maintained, fully serviced, and comfortable all-wheel-drive wagon that doesnt compromise on practicality or style. If you want a vehicle thats ready to go, well cared for, and built for real life, this one deserves a closer look. Come shop at Carter Subaru Today!

description: Fox Subaru of Macomb is proud to offer this bold and adventure-ready 2025 Subaru Outback Onyx Edition in Ice Silver Metallic, a top choice for shoppers searching for a certified pre-owned Subaru Outback Onyx with low miles and premium features. This One Owner, Clean Carfax Outback is Subaru Certified and includes an exceptional 7-year or 100,000-mile Powertrain Warranty, delivering confidence and long-term value. Designed with rugged style and refined comfort, this Outback Onyx Edition features heated front seats, a heated steering wheel, a power driver seat, and a power moonroof for year-round driving enjoyment. The Popular Package #2 adds sought-after upgrades including a power liftgate, auto-dimming exterior mirrors with approach lights, LED lighting upgrades, and protective features like a rear bumper cover, rear seatback protector, and splash guards. The aggressive look is completed by 18-inch black aluminum-alloy wheels, perfectly matching the Onyx Editions signature blacked-out design. With Subaru Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive, advanced safety technology, and the versatility that makes the Outback one of the most searched-for midsize SUVs, this 2025 Subaru Outback Onyx Edition is an outstanding option for drivers looking for capability, style, and certified Subaru reliability.

description:
Discover the exceptional 2024 Subaru Impreza Sport, a versatile and well-equipped compact car that seamlessly blends performance, technology, and style. With its sleek gray exterior and impressive 2.0L DOHC engine paired with the reliable Lineartronic CVT and Subaru's renowned Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive, this Impreza Sport is ready to elevate your driving experience.

Key features of this well-appointed Impreza Sport include:

11.6" Subaru STARLINK Multimedia Plus System with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration
Dual-zone automatic climate control
Rearview camera with dynamic guidelines
Steering wheel-mounted audio controls
Keyless entry with push-button start
Subaru EyeSight Driver Assist Technology
Blind Spot Detection with Lane Change Assist and Rear Cross-Traffic Alert

With an EPA-estimated 27 mpg in the city and 34 mpg on the highway, this Impreza Sport delivers exceptional fuel efficiency to help you conquer your daily commute or weekend adventures. The spacious interior, with its split-folding rear seats, offers ample room for passengers and cargo, making it the perfect companion for your active lifestyle.

Subaru's commitment to safety is evident in the Impreza Sport, which features a comprehensive suite of advanced safety technologies, including Dual Front, Side, and Curtain Airbags, as well as the STARLINK Safety and Security system for added peace of mind.

Experience the perfect blend of performance, technology, and utility in the 2024 Subaru Impreza Sport. With a list price of $21,750, this exceptional compact car represents exceptional value and is sure to exceed your expectations. Visit our showroom today to take it for a test drive and discover why the Impreza Sport should be your next vehicle.

Our 2024 Subaru Outback Touring AWD masters every mile with legendary capability in striking Cosmic Blue Pearl! Powered by a 2.5 Liter BOXER 4 Cylinder delivering 182hp to a paddle-shifted Lineartronic CVT. This All Wheel Drive SUV combines that muscle with Subaru's X-MODE system for impressive traction and still returns nearly 32mpg on the highway. Styled to stand out, our Outback boasts a power sunroof, hands-free liftgate, LED lighting, steering-responsive headlamps, fog lamps, alloy wheels, roof rails, and Satin Chrome mirror caps.

Serious comfort awaits in our Touring cabin, which is smartly engineered for better adventures. First-class amenities include heated/ventilated Nappa leather power front and heated rear seats, a heated leather steering wheel, dual-zone automatic climate control, and keyless entry/ignition. Subaru helps satisfy your infotainment needs with Harman Kardon audio, an 11.6-inch touchscreen, full-color navigation, wireless Android Auto/Apple CarPlay, WiFi compatibility, and Bluetooth.

For safety's sake, Subaru supplies front/rear automatic braking, blind-spot monitoring, automatic emergency steering, adaptive cruise control, lane-keeping assistance, front/rear camera systems, automatic collision notification, and other high-tech features. You can go where love takes you in our Outback Touring! Save this Page and Call for Availability. We Know You Will Enjoy Your TINDOL Test Drive Towards Ownership!

description:
The 2024 Kia Soul LX is a versatile and well-equipped compact SUV that's perfect for your daily commute or weekend adventures. With its spacious interior, impressive fuel efficiency, and advanced technology features, this vehicle is an exceptional value in the crowded crossover market.

Highlights of this Soul LX include:
LX Technology Package with Blind-Spot Collision-Avoidance Assist, Lane Change Assist, and Rear Cross-Traffic Collision Avoidance Assist
6.5J x 16" Alloy Wheels
Carpeted Floor Mats

Under the hood, you'll find a 2.0L I4 DOHC engine paired with a smooth-shifting CVT transmission, delivering an EPA-estimated 29 MPG in the city and 35 MPG on the highway. This powertrain provides a responsive and efficient driving experience, whether you're navigating city streets or cruising down the highway.

The interior of the Soul LX is thoughtfully designed with your comfort and convenience in mind. Enjoy features like air conditioning, power windows, remote keyless entry, and steering wheel-mounted audio controls. The 6-speaker audio system with AM/FM radio, MP3 playback, and HD Radio keeps you entertained on the road.

Safety is also a top priority, with the Soul LX offering a suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies. Dual front impact airbags, dual front side impact airbags, and an overhead airbag provide comprehensive protection in the event of a collision. The 4-wheel disc brakes with ABS and electronic stability control help you maintain control in challenging driving conditions.

Whether you're looking for a practical daily driver or a versatile companion for your active lifestyle, the 2024 Kia Soul LX is an excellent choice. Its combination of style, functionality, and value make it a compelling option in the compact SUV segment.

description: This 2024 Subaru Impreza Sport delivers the perfect blend of everyday practicality, sporty style, and all-weather confidence exactly what Pacific Northwest drivers are looking for. Powered by Subarus efficient BOXER engine and legendary Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive, the Impreza feels planted and confident whether youre navigating wet city streets, heading over mountain passes, or just enjoying the daily commute. The Sport trim adds a bold, athletic look along with a well-appointed interior designed for comfort and convenience. The power moonroof opens up the cabin with fresh air and natural light, while the All-Weather Package makes year-round driving easier with features built to handle cold mornings and unpredictable conditions. Blind Spot Detection with Rear Cross Traffic Alert adds an extra layer of confidence, helping you stay aware of surrounding traffic on busy roads and in tight parking lots. Compact, responsive, and easy to live with, the Impreza Sport offers impressive fuel efficiency without sacrificing capability or safety. Its a smart choice for drivers who want a fun-to-drive hatchback thats as reliable as it is versatile. Now available at Carter Subaru in Shoreline, where doing the right thing still matters. Come shop at Carter Subaru Today!

The Outback Premium's interior is a sanctuary of comfort and convenience. Sink into the heated front bucket seats and enjoy the premium cloth upholstery, while the 11.6-inch STARLINK Multimedia Plus system provides seamless connectivity and intuitive control of your entertainment and navigation needs. The split-folding rear seat offers versatile cargo space, ensuring you can easily accommodate your gear for any adventure.

Safety is a top priority in the Outback Premium, with a suite of advanced driver-assistance features, including Automatic High-Beam Headlights, Front Fog Lights, and a Rear Window Wiper. The Subaru EyeSight Driver Assist Technology and Rear-Vision Camera further enhance your confidence on the road, helping you navigate with ease.

The spacious interior offers ample room for your gear, with a power liftgate and 60/40 split-folding rear seats for added versatility.

Whether you're tackling rugged terrain or navigating the city streets, the 2024 Subaru Outback Premium is the perfect blend of capability, technology, and comfort. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today. We're confident you'll be impressed by this exceptional SUV.

Our knowledgeable sales team is here to answer any questions you may have and help you find the perfect Subaru to fit your needs. Visit us today and let us show you why the Outback Premium is the ideal choice for your next vehicle.

Mileage is unlimited. OTHER NOTABLE FEATURES AND OPTIONS YOU SHOULD KNOW ABOUT: PINE GREY METALLIC Advanced Package ($1,900 value)
  • Graphical Head-Up Display (HUD)
  • Pilot Assist Driver Assistance System
  • 360 Surround View Camera
  • Interior High Level Illumination
  • Inductive Charging For Smart Phone
Safety and Security
  • The vehicle is equipped with a system that senses, and then prepares, the vehicle and/or occupants, for an impending forward collision.
  • The vehicle constantly monitors the roadway in front of the vehicle and identifies and tracks pedestrians on an interior display. If the system determines a likely impact, it will automatically take preventative steps to avoid hitting the pedestrian.
  • With this system the driver's hands must remain on the wheel at all times but can be removed briefly (for a few seconds), otherwise the vehicle will prompt the driver to put their hands back on the wheel.
Technology and Telematics
  • Without the need for a manufacturer specific app to be installed on the smart device, the vehicle infotainment system can access and control functions of a smart device physically plugged-into the vehicle.
  • Mobile devices can wirelessly connect to the internet through the vehicle's private mobile network.

Discover the perfect blend of rugged capability and refined sophistication in the 2020 Subaru Outback Touring. This exceptional SUV is the embodiment of Subaru's commitment to engineering excellence, offering a seamless balance of performance, comfort, and advanced technology.

Elevate your driving experience with the Outback Touring's impressive list of features:

Wireless Charger
Auto-Dimming Exterior Mirror with Approach Light
Rear Bumper Cover
All-Weather Floor Liners
Windshield Sunshade
Dome Light LED Upgrade
Navigation System
12 Speakers
Harman/Kardon Surround Sound Speaker System
Subaru STARLINK 11.6" Multimedia Nav System
Power Moonroof
Power Liftgate
Steering Wheel Paddle Shift Control Switches
Wireless Charger
18" x 7J Black Aluminum Alloy Wheels

Beneath the sleek exterior, the Outback Touring is powered by a robust 2.5L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V engine, paired with a CVT Lineartronic transmission and Subaru's renowned Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive system. This combination delivers an exceptional blend of power and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 26 city/33 highway MPG.

Comfort and convenience are at the forefront, with features like dual-zone automatic climate control, heated and ventilated front seats, a heated steering wheel, and a power driver's seat with memory function. The Nappa leather-trimmed upholstery and premium sound system create an unparalleled driving experience.

Safety is also a top priority, with advanced driver-assistance technologies such as Brake Assist, Electronic Stability Control, and Rear Camera. The Outback Touring is engineered to provide you and your loved ones with the utmost protection on the road.

This 2020 Subaru Outback Touring, with its low mileage of 61,274, represents an exceptional value. Experience the perfect balance of capability, comfort, and technology by scheduling a test drive today. We're confident you'll be impressed by this remarkable SUV.

Safety is a top priority in the Volvo V60, with advanced features like City Safety automatic braking, blind spot monitoring, and adaptive cruise control. Plus, the V60 has earned top safety ratings, giving you peace of mind on every journey.

Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this 2015 Volvo V60 T6 R-Design Platinum. With its combination of style, performance, and safety, it's the perfect choice for drivers who demand the best. Come take a test drive today and experience the excellence of the V60 for yourself.

description:
Built for the Wild: 2022 Subaru Outback Wilderness in Ice Silver Metallic
Adventure has a new look. This 2022 Subaru Outback Wilderness is the most capable Outback ever built, designed specifically for those who leave the pavement behind. Dressed in the crisp Ice Silver Metallic, this AWD powerhouse combines Subaru's legendary reliability with factory-installed off-road upgrades.

With a Clean CARFAX and a suite of "Wilderness-only" features, this Recent Arrival is ready to go from the carpool lane to the mountain pass without missing a beat.

Exclusive Wilderness Capability:
Elevated Ground Clearance: Boasting 9.5 inches of ground clearance (nearly an inch more than the standard Outback) and a front skid plate to tackle rocks and ruts with ease.

Turbocharged Performance: Powered by a 2.4L Turbocharged SUBARU BOXER engine delivering 260 horsepower and 277 lb-ft of torque, allowing for a robust 3,500-lb towing capacity.

Off-Road Suspension

Advanced Dual-Function X-MODE: Includes specialized settings for Snow/Dirt and Deep Snow/Mud, optimizing the AWD system for maximum traction in the toughest conditions.

Rugged Interior & Technology:
Adventure-Ready Upholstery: Features StarTex water-repellent upholstery with copper-finish stitching and embossed Wilderness logosdesigned to be durable and easy to clean after a day in the dirt.

Subaru STARLINK 11.6" Navigation: A massive vertical tablet-style display with Navigation, Wireless Charging, and Apple CarPlay/Android Auto integration.

Cargo Protection: Equipped with a Rear Seat Back Protector, Cargo Sidewall Protectors, and all-weather floor mats to keep the interior pristine regardless of your gear.

Wilderness Accents: Unique Anodized Copper-finish interior accents and a heated steering wheel add a touch of rugged luxury.

Safety & Utility:
EyeSight Driver Assist: Specially re-tuned for the vehicle's higher ride height, including Adaptive Cruise Control, Lane Keep Assist, and Pre-Collision Braking.

Enhanced Roof Rails: High-capacity fixed ladder-type roof rails can support up to 700 lbs (static), making them perfect for a rooftop tent.

180-Degree Front View Monitor: A front-facing camera helps you see obstacles on the trail that are usually hidden from the drivers seat.

Ready for Your Next Expedition?

Call or Text Peterson BMW of Boise today at 208-378-5980 to schedule your test drive!



All advertised vehicles are subject to actual dealer availability. Certain vehicles listed may not be available or may have different prices. Prices exclude state tax, license, document preparation fee ($499), and finance charges (if applicable). Vehicle options and pricing are subject to change. Pricing and availability vary by dealership. Please check with your dealer for more information.

description:
Experience the pinnacle of luxury and capability with the 2023 Lexus GX 460 Luxury. This exceptional SUV combines sophisticated design, uncompromising performance, and an array of advanced features to elevate your driving experience.

Boasting a striking exterior in Black, the GX 460 Luxury commands attention on the road. Under the hood, a powerful 4.6L V8 DOHC Dual VVT-i 32V engine, paired with a 6-Speed Automatic with Sequential Shift ECT, delivers an exhilarating drive with 4WD capability. Enjoy impressive fuel efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 15 MPG in the city and 19 MPG on the highway.

Navigation system: Lexus Enform Dynamic Navigation
17 Speakers
Premium audio system: Mark Levinson
Lexus Multimedia System with Navigation
Adaptive suspension
Auto-leveling suspension
4-Wheel Disc Brakes
Anti-whiplash front head restraints
Dual front impact airbags
Dual front side impact airbags
Emergency communication system: Safety Connect (3-year trial)
Power moonroof

Step inside the meticulously crafted cabin and experience unparalleled comfort and convenience. Indulge in the luxurious Semi-Aniline Leather Seat Trim, with Heated & Ventilated Front Bucket Seats and Heated Rear Seats. The Lexus Multimedia System with Navigation and 17-Speaker Premium Audio System provide a captivating entertainment experience, while the Adaptive Suspension and Auto-Leveling Suspension ensure a smooth and composed ride.

Safety is paramount in the GX 460 Luxury, with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver assistance technologies, including Blind Spot Monitoring, Rear Cross-Traffic Alert, and Lane Departure Alert with Steering Assist. You can drive with confidence, knowing your family is protected.

Elevate your driving experience with the 2023 Lexus GX 460 Luxury. Discover the perfect blend of luxury, performance, and technology that will exceed your expectations. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate why the GX 460 Luxury is the ultimate choice for the discerning SUV enthusiast.

description: Our 2023 Subaru Outback Premium in Ice Silver Metallic is a versatile, confidence-inspiring wagon with just 19,121 miles. This vehicle comes with a SMARTCare Maintenance Plan that includes 2 years/25,000 miles of oil changes, tire rotations, and roadside assistance, and the purchase also includes the remainder of the original manufacturer's warranty for added peace of mind. With Subaru's renowned All-Wheel Drive system, this Outback is ready for changing weather, road trips, and everyday commuting alike.Inside, you'll find a comfortable and practical cabin finished in slate black cloth upholstery with subtle silver stitching. The 11.6-inch Subaru STARLINK multimedia navigation system is the centerpiece, offering wireless Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, Bluetooth connectivity, HD Radio, SiriusXM capability, and intuitive voice-activated controls. Convenience features like keyless access with push-button start, a hands-free power rear gate, power moonroof, heated front seats, and a power driver's seat make every drive more enjoyable.Safety is a strong suit with blind spot detection, rear cross-traffic alert, adaptive cruise control, lane keep assist, driver monitoring, and a backup camera. With ample cargo space, roof rails, and a smooth ride, this Outback Premium is ready to handle whatever your lifestyle demands.

The standard navigation system, Apple CarPlay, and Android Auto integration keep you connected and entertained, while the dual-zone automatic climate control ensures everyone rides in comfort.

Safety is a top priority in the Kia Soul EX, with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies, including automatic emergency braking, lane-keep assist, and a rearview camera with dynamic parking guidelines. Whether you're navigating the city streets or embarking on a weekend adventure, the 2023 Kia Soul EX is the perfect companion. Discover the exceptional 2023 Subaru Outback Premium, a versatile and well-equipped SUV that's ready to elevate your driving experience. This meticulously maintained Outback boasts a suite of advanced features designed to enhance your daily commute and weekend adventures.

Blind Spot Detection (BSD) with Rear Cross-Traffic Alert (RCTA)
Keyless Access with Push-Button Start
Auto-Dimming Mirror with Compass and HomeLink
All-Weather Floor Liners

Powered by a robust 2.5L 4-cylinder DOHC 16V engine paired with Subaru's renowned Lineartronic CVT and Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive, this Outback delivers an exceptional balance of performance and efficiency. With an EPA-estimated 26 MPG in the city and 32 MPG on the highway, you'll enjoy the perfect blend of power and fuel economy.

Step inside the spacious and well-appointed cabin, where you'll be surrounded by premium amenities. The Subaru STARLINK 11.6-inch Multimedia Plus system provides seamless connectivity, while the dual-zone automatic climate control ensures a comfortable ride for all. The hands-free power rear gate and Blind Spot Detection with Rear Cross-Traffic Alert add convenience and safety to your daily routine.

Designed with your active lifestyle in mind, the 2023 Subaru Outback Premium offers ample cargo space and a durable, all-weather capability. Whether you're tackling rugged terrain, navigating urban streets, or embarking on a family road trip, this versatile SUV is up for the challenge.

Experience the exceptional craftsmanship and advanced technology that make the 2023 Subaru Outback Premium a standout in its class. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this remarkable vehicle can enhance your driving experience. We're confident you'll be impressed by its impressive features and uncompromising quality.

Our One Owner, Accident Free 2022 Toyota 4Runner Limited 4WD in Barcelona Red Metallic knows how to treat you right! Powered by a 4.0 Liter V6 generating 270hp paired to a 5 Speed Automatic transmission for premium capability. This Four Wheel Drive SUV also features an X-REAS sports suspension for enhanced performance even on challenging terrain, and it sees nearly 19mpg on the highway. You'll love how our 4Runner feels ready for anything and looks fantastic with LED lighting, fog lamps, a power sunroof, 20-inch alloy wheels, chrome accents, roof rails, hitch, a full skid plate, and heated power mirrors with built-in turn signals.

Take on your next adventure with top-notch comfort in our Limited cabin, which provides perforated leather heated/ventilated power front seats, a leather-wrapped steering wheel, dual-zone automatic climate control, Smart Key access, and pushbutton start. Advanced technology helps keep you connected with an 8-inch touchscreen, full-color navigation, Android Auto/Apple CarPlay, Amazon Alexa/WiFi compatibility, and a 15-speaker JBL sound system.

A backup camera and innovative Toyota Safety Sense technology, including adaptive cruise control, lane departure alert, automatic emergency braking, and pedestrian detection, help you stay out of harm's way. Our 4Runner Limited puts your needs first! Save this Page and Call for Availability. We Know You Will Enjoy Your Grand Valley Auto Sales Test Drive Towards Ownership!

This 2025 Nissan Pathfinder Platinum delivers premium comfort, powerful performance, and modern techall at an exceptional value. With just 6,954 miles and CARFAX 1-Owner history, this Nissan Pathfinder offers peace of mind and long-term reliability. The V6 3.5L gasoline engine and 4WD system provide confident towing and sure-footed handling in varied Georgia weather and road conditions. description:
Introducing the 2011 Subaru Outback 2.5i, the perfect combination of style, performance, and versatility. This rugged yet refined crossover SUV is ready to take on any adventure you throw its way. With its spacious interior, advanced safety features, and impressive fuel efficiency, the Outback 2.5i is the ultimate vehicle for both daily commutes and weekend getaways.

Step inside and experience the comfort of the Outback's plush seats and ample legroom. The spacious cargo area provides plenty of room for all your gear, making it a great choice for families, outdoor enthusiasts, and anyone in need of extra storage space. The Outback's durable build and all-wheel drive system make it capable of handling any terrain, from city streets to off-road trails.

Under the hood, you'll find a reliable 2.5-liter four-cylinder engine, delivering smooth and efficient performance. With an EPA-estimated 22 MPG in the city and 29 MPG on the highway, you'll save money at the pump while enjoying a powerful driving experience. Plus, the Outback's Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive system provides superior traction and handling in all weather conditions.

Safety is a top priority in the Outback, which is why it comes equipped with features like stability control, antilock brakes, and a comprehensive airbag system. The 2011 model also received top safety ratings from the IIHS and NHTSA, giving you peace of mind on the road.

Don't miss your chance to own this 2011 Subaru Outback 2.5i. With its exceptional performance, spacious interior, and rugged design, it's the perfect vehicle for anyone seeking adventure and practicality. Come take a test drive today and see for yourself why the Outback is a top choice for crossover SUVs.

description: 2011 Subaru Outback 2.5i Premium  2.5L H4 PZEV, 170 hp / 170 ft-lb This Outback is powered by Subarus 2.5L horizontally opposed four-cylinder PZEV engine producing 170 hp and 170 ft-lbs of torque, paired with Subarus full-time Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive system. It delivers an EPA-rated 22 MPG city and 29 MPG highway. The odometer is below 128,000 miles, averaging under 8,000 miles per year. The vehicle is in excellent overall condition, has a clean CARFAX, and has had one owner. Factory standard features (2.5i Premium) include: - Powertrain & driveline: 2.5L Boxer H4 PZEV engine, Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive for improved traction and stability. - Exterior: 17-inch alloy wheels, roof rails with integrated crossbars for cargo carrying, fog lights, heated power outside mirrors, rear wiper, and halogen headlamps. - Safety & driver aids: Anti-lock Braking System (ABS) with Electronic Brakeforce Distribution, Vehicle Dynamics Control (stability control) and traction control, front and side-impact airbags plus side curtain airbags, active front head restraints, and Tire Pressure Monitoring System (TPMS). Child seat LATCH anchors are included. - Comfort & convenience: Power windows and door locks with remote keyless entry, cruise control, tilt/telescoping steering column, and a center armrest with storage. Front seats are heated, the drivers seat is power-adjustable and the rear seat folds 60/40 to expand cargo capacity. - Interior & cargo: Durable cloth seating surfaces, comfortable passenger space with well-laid-out controls, and a roomy cargo area with tie-downs and a cargo cover. - Climate: Manual air conditioning with cabin filtration and rear ventilation for passengers. - Audio & connectivity: AM/FM/CD audio system with auxiliary input (and MP3 compatibility), steering-wheel mounted audio controls, and multiple speakers for a balanced cabin sound. - Construction & convenience features: Subarus reinforced chassis design for occupant protection, extensive corrosion protection and practical features like rear cargo access and easy-fold rear seats. This Outback combines Subarus practical versatility and safety features with a well-maintained low-mileage example. The clean CARFAX and single-owner history support the vehicles excellent overall condition. If you would like specific equipment verification (option packages or factory supplements), a detailed inspection or a look at the window sticker or build sheet can confirm any factory-installed options. Frontier Sales & Service 2575 State Route 72 Jonestown, PA 17038 (717) 867-8474

More information about the 2017 Subaru Outback: The genius of the Outback has always been its ability to straddle classifications, it helped create the crossover segment in the 1990s. With better off-road credentials and a more usable luggage compartment, the Outback offers increased versatility over plain Jane family sedans. At the same time, the Subaru Outback offers the kind of fuel economy that most mid-sized SUVs struggle to match. This model sets itself apart with fuel-efficient transmissions, standard all-wheel drive, good ground clearance, Versatility, and spacious interior

description: Discover spacious versatility, dependable performance and everyday practicality in this 2015 Dodge Durango SXT, now available at BMW of West Houston. Designed to accommodate families and active lifestyles, the Durango SXT offers three-row seating, confident road manners and the flexibility needed for daily driving and weekend adventures alike.The Dodge Durango SXT delivers smooth and capable performance that makes commuting and long-distance travel comfortable and controlled. Its stable ride quality and responsive handling provide confidence on city streets and highways, while its SUV design offers the strength and presence drivers appreciate. Engineered for versatility, this Durango is well suited for hauling passengers, cargo or gear with ease.Inside, the cabin is thoughtfully designed to maximize comfort and usability. Supportive seating, a practical layout and intuitive controls create a welcoming environment for both driver and passengers. **4D Sport Utility | 4WD | 75th Anniversary Edition**

Celebrate Jeep heritage with this **2017 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Sahara 75th Anniversary Edition**, finished in Granite Crystal Metallic Clearcoat and equipped with distinctive bronze accents throughout. With the **odometer reading 14,174 miles below market average**, this Wrangler stands out for both value and collectability.

description:
This 2018 Bentley Continental GTC W12 in Glacier White over white interior with only 25,595 miles is a refined and powerful open top grand tourer, powered by a 6.0 liter twin turbo W12 engine producing 626 horsepower and 664 pound feet of torque, paired with an 8 speed dual clutch transmission and all wheel drive that propels it from 0 to 60 miles per hour in about 3.9 seconds with a governed top speed near 207 miles per hour. Weighing approximately 5300 pounds, the GTC W12 combines effortless long distance cruising with dynamic capability, aided by adaptive air suspension and all wheel steering for confident handling and a smooth ride. Inside, the cabin is luxuriously appointed with hand stitched leather, heated and ventilated seats, premium audio and advanced infotainment, while the convertible soft top opens quickly to offer open air motoring. This low mileage example represents the consummate blend of performance, craftsmanship and everyday usability that defines Bentley's flagship convertible. Why BUY from Naples Motorsports Inc.? When you choose this Glacier White 2018 Bentley Continental GT with 25,597 miles, you are not just buying a used vehicle - you are investing in quality, reliability and peace of mind. Our clientele depend on us for Transparent Pricing, Convenience and, most importantly, Customer FIRST Service! No Accidents! What this vehicle includes: Convenience
  • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
  • Power close trunk/liftgate - Dump the slam. You're done loading up, now don't subject your passengers to the ear splitting sound of you slamming the back shut. All you have to do is hit the button and the power close trunk/liftgate takes care of the rest. You can walk away as the Power close trunk/liftgate gently closes and latches.
  • Power open and close trunk - On-demand access. When your arms are full of cargo, the last thing you want to do is set it all down just to open the trunk, then pick it all back up to load it in. By remotely opening and closing, power trunk lets you skip straight to the loading. Then you can walk away as it gently closes and latches. Load and go with power open and close trunk.
Safety and Security
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
Come on in to Naples Motorsports Inc. today at 1250 Airport-Pulling Rd S Naples FL 34104 or call (239) 430-5655 to schedule a test drive!

description:
**2018 Ferrari 488 Spider RWD**

This 2018 Ferrari 488 Spider is a rear-wheel-drive, mid-engine supercar that blends razor-sharp performance with the drama of open-top driving. As the convertible version of the 488 GTB, the Spider delivers the same twin-turbocharged V8 performance with the added theater of a power-retractable hardtop.

Power comes from Ferraris 3.9-liter twin-turbo V8, an engine widely regarded as one of the greatest of the modern era for its immediacy, balance, and unmistakable sound. Paired with a rapid-shifting dual-clutch transmission, the 488 Spider offers explosive acceleration and precise control, while adaptive suspension and Ferraris advanced chassis electronics keep the car composed at any speed. Carbon-ceramic brakes provide exceptional stopping power and confidence.

The retractable hardtop operates seamlessly, preserving the coupes lines when closed and transforming the driving experience when lowered. With the roof down, the car delivers an immersive connection to the engine and surroundings, making the 488 Spider as thrilling on a scenic drive as it is capable on a winding road.

Inside, the cockpit is purpose-built yet refined, featuring leather-trimmed sport bucket seats, a leather-wrapped sport steering wheel, dual-zone automatic climate control, and Ferraris infotainment system with navigation and Apple CarPlay. Premium touches such as Harman/Kardon audio, rain-sensing wipers, headlight cleaning system, and integrated rollover protection enhance both comfort and safety.

Additional highlights include rear parking sensors, adaptive suspension, power seats and windows, speed-sensitive steering, and staggered 20-inch alloy wheels that emphasize the cars low, aggressive stance.

The 488 Spider represents a pivotal moment in Ferraris lineage, combining turbocharged performance with classic Ferrari design and open-air excitement. It remains one of the most engaging and emotionally compelling modern Ferraris, offering supercar performance without compromise and an ownership experience defined by drama, precision, and unmistakable presence.


Clean CARFAX.

description: Ferrari South Bay is thrilled to offer this beautiful "delivery-mile" 488 Spider, finished in Classic Rosso Corsa with equally-classic Cuoio leather interior. With only 59 miles since initial delivery, this 488 Spider is all but technically new! The exterior is finished in Ferrari's iconic Rosso Corsa and has Scuderia Ferrari Shields proudly positioned on the front fenders. 20" Forged Diamond-Cut wheels surround Carbon Ceramic Brakes with Red Calipers. The Interior of this 488 Spider is trimmed in time-honored Cuoio Leather accented with Rosso. This 488 Spider is offered complete with both keys, tools, car cover and battery tender. It has passed Ferrari's 101-Point Certification and is eligible for Ferrari's Power16 Warranty at time of purchase. If you'd like to know more about this sensational 488 Spider, please contact one of our knowledgeable sales staff. Ferrari South Bay is proudly part of Holand Automotive Group, one of North Americas leading luxury automotive retailers. We offer nationwide shipping, trade-in opportunities, financing, client consignments, and world-class delivery service. Contact us today to explore ownership of this remarkable Ferrari. Please visit us at 23305 Hawthorne Blvd, Torrance, CA 90505, or call us at (888) 578-8767.

description: Ferrari South Bay is pleased to bring to market this gorgeous BMW Z8, finished in Titanium Silver with Black leather and a nice selection of very desirable and rare Dinan performance upgrades. With just 2 owners from new, each with long term ownership, it's easy to tell it's been driven with care. Having just received new tires and new hardtop headliner in Alcantara, this very collectible Ultimate Driving Machine is ready to rip up a canyon or deliver you to Bimmerfest in style! The exterior of this Z8 is finished in classic Titanium Silver and sports 20" Alpina Wheels and Alpina center caps. The car has been fitted with the all-important Performance Package securing the strut towers, as well as ultra rare Dinan upgrades including Exhaust Headers, High Flow Mass Meters with Airboxes, High Flow Throttle Bodies and Tuned Velocity Stacks, Stage 5 software and Dinan Pedals which were all professionally installed in early 2011. The car comes with it's original hard top and hard top stand, as well. The interior is trimmed in All Leather Nappa Black leather with silver accents. Very little equipment was "optional" on the Z8, and this car is equipped with the original BMW phone, Xenon Headlights, Neon Tail Lights, Harmon Kardon 10-Speaker Audio w/6-disk changer, Power Soft Top, Power Steering Column and Windows, and 6-Way Electric Seats. The drivers seat is free of the crack commonly found near the seat controls, the seatbacks are snugly tucked against the seats, and the neon turn indicators work flawlessly. This Z8 is offered complete with both original keys, books, tools, two keys, and Original Removable Hard Top, as well as partial service records and the original window sticker. If you'd like to find out more about modern classic, please call or visit our showroom to experience it for yourself. Please reach out to our knowledgeable sales staff. Ferrari South Bay is proudly part of Holand Automotive Group, one of North Americas leading luxury automotive retailers. We offer nationwide shipping, trade-in opportunities, financing, client consignments, and world-class delivery service. Contact us today to explore ownership of this remarkable Ferrari. Please visit us at 23305 Hawthorne Blvd, Torrance, CA 90505, or call us at (888) 578-8767.

description: Check out this pre-owned 2013 Porsche 911 we recently got in. This sporty Porsche 911 convertible leads the class in performance and refinement. Today's luxury vehicle is not just about opulence. It's about a perfect balance of performance, comfort and attention to detail. This 2013 Porsche 911 Turbo is the perfect example of the modern luxury. This AWD-equipped vehicle will handle beautifully on any terrain and in any weather condition your may find yourself in. The benefits of driving an all wheel drive vehicle, such as this Porsche 911 Turbo, include superior acceleration, improved steering, and increased traction and stability. This low mileage Porsche 911 has barely been touched. It's the next best thing to buying new. More information about the 2013 Porsche 911: In the world of high-end sports cars, the 911 is the most iconic choice, with 50 years of evolution under its belt. Though the design continues to change, the fundamentals are still in place: rear-mounted flat-six engine and a precision chassis developed with handling in mind. Together, the components make for a sports car that's hard to beat both in terms of aesthetics and performance, as well as history. It's arguably a capable competitor for the Aston Martin V8 Vantage, Audi R8, BMW M3 and Nissan GT-R. This model sets itself apart with available all-wheel drive, exceptional agility, convertible options, surprising fuel efficiency, top-level engine performance, and Iconic design with a fresh spin Come join our family at Lamborghini Palm Beach, where your buying experience is most important to us.

Whether you're cruising down a coastal road with the top down or navigating city streets, this vehicle ensures every journey is memorable.

2023 Chevrolet Corvette Stingray 3LT with Z51 Performance Package, 6.2L V8 power, CARFAX 1-Owner personal vehicle, and just under 3,000 miles.

This Corvette Stingray 3LT pairs a thrilling 6.2L V8 with rear-wheel drive and an 8-speed dual-clutch transmission for sharp acceleration and precise control. EPA-rated 16 city and 24 highway MPG balance supercar performance with real-world drivability. Para la version en espanol, vea abajo.

The 3LT trim elevates the experience with premium materials, advanced infotainment, and a driver-focused cockpit. Performance features from the Z51 package enhance handling and braking, making this convertible ideal for spirited drives and weekend getaways.

The 2023 Corvette Stingray continues its legacy as one of the most celebrated American sports cars, praised for delivering exotic-level performance with everyday usability and standout design.

Why buy from us? We offer a transparent, no-pressure experience supported by a thorough reconditioning process. Our expert team is here to answer questions clearly and help you feel confident from start to finish. Manufacturer warranty coverage may still apply.

Ready to take the next step? Contact us today to schedule a no-obligation test drive or request additional details. Were committed to making your experience smooth, informative, and rewarding.

2023 Chevrolet Corvette Stingray 3LT con paquete Z51 Performance, motor V8 de 6.2L, vehiculo personal de un solo dueno segun CARFAX y poco menos de 3,000 millas.

Este Corvette Stingray 3LT combina un potente V8 de 6.2L con traccion trasera y transmision de doble embrague de 8 velocidades para una respuesta rapida y manejo preciso. Ofrece un consumo estimado por la EPA de 16 en ciudad y 24 en carretera.

La version 3LT destaca por su interior premium, tecnologia avanzada y un diseno centrado en el conductor. El paquete Z51 mejora el desempeno dinamico, ideal para quienes buscan emociones fuertes al volante.

El Corvette Stingray 2023 mantiene su reputacion como un icono de los deportivos estadounidenses, reconocido por ofrecer alto desempeno, estilo distintivo y facilidad de uso diario.

Por que comprar con nosotros? Brindamos un proceso transparente y sin presion, respaldado por una inspeccion completa del vehiculo. Nuestro equipo esta listo para ayudarte con claridad y confianza. La cobertura de garantia del fabricante aun puede aplicar.

description:
Land Rover Riverside is delighted to showcase, this Pre-Owned 2023 Lexus LC 500 Convertible Dressed in an evocative Atomic Silver and with just 35,284 miles to its name, this vehicle is a testament to the potent combination of high performance and sophistication that Lexus embodies.
The LC 500 Convertible stands as a beacon of design and performance, its Atomic Silver exterior not just a color, but a symbol of cutting-edge luxury. It features a power soft top with active roll bars, 20-inch 10-spoke cast alloy wheels with run-flat tires, and triple-beam LED headlamps that blend aggressive design with functional brilliance. Power-folding, auto-dimming, and heated outer mirrors complete its bold exterior presence.

Step inside and the driver-focused interior welcomes you with heated and ventilated leather-trimmed power-adjustable front seats, complemented by the SmartAccess system and a push-button start for added convenience. The Touring Package adds semi-aniline leather seats, embossed headrests, windshield de-icer, heated steering wheel, Climate Concierge with upper body heating, and a Mark Levinson 13-speaker Reference Surround Sound Audio System for a truly immersive experience.

Engine and Performance: At the heart of this performance icon is a naturally aspirated 5.0-liter V8 engine that roars to life with 471 horsepower and 398 lb-ft of torque. Mated to a 10-speed Sport Direct Shift automatic transmission with magnesium paddle shifters, and rear-wheel drive configuration, the LC 500 offers an exhilarating drive. The Torsen limited-slip differential and Yamaha rear performance damper enhance traction and responsiveness, while adaptive variable suspension ensures a composed yet dynamic ride.

Key Features:

Touring Package: Includes 21" wheels, semi-aniline leather-trimmed front seats, Climate Concierge, embossed headrests, and a 13-speaker Mark Levinson audio system.

Head-Up Display: Projects vital information directly onto the windshield, keeping your focus on the road.

Carbon Fiber Scuff Plates: Add a touch of motorsport styling and durability to the entryway.

Lexus Safety System+: Features Pre-Collision System with Pedestrian Detection, Dynamic Radar Cruise Control, Intelligent High Beam Headlamps, Lane Keep Assist, and Lane Departure Alert.

Lexus Navigation with 10.3 Display: Paired with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto for seamless connectivity and ease of use.

Blind Spot Monitor and Rear Cross-Traffic Alert: Provides peace of mind while changing lanes or reversing.

This 2023 Lexus LC 500 Convertible is far more than just a luxury grand tourer, it is the embodiment of Lexus philosophy of exhilarating performance and timeless elegance. Available at Land Rover Riverside, this vehicle offers an invitation to experience the art of driving in its most captivating form.



Land Rover Riverside is a member of the indiGO Auto Group. Our dealership features a beautiful Land Rover Corporate Identity showroom, fully staffed factory certified service center, parts department, finance department, detail department, and Land Rover accessories boutique. Allow us to also help arrange transportation of your new car directly to your home anywhere in the world. Trade-in proposals are always welcome. If you like this vehicle and have questions, simply call, email, or drop by our location at 8051 Auto Dr, Riverside, CA 92504. We invite you to Activate Your Ownership with us today!

description: *Why BUY from Mercedes-Benz Of Omaha?*When you choose this *Starfire Pearl 2013 Lexus CT 200h Hybrid* with *54,072* miles, you are not just buying a used vehicle - you are investing in quality, reliability and peace of mind. Our clientele depend on us for *Transparent Pricing, Convenience* and, most importantly, *Customer FIRST Service! No Doc Fees. No Add-Ons. No Suprises!**What this vehicle includes:*=== Comfort === * This upholstery simulates leather, is durable and easy to keep clean.=== Convenience === * Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.=== Exterior and Appearance === * First-row sunroof - Let more of the outside in. Now you can be in the sun or gaze at the stars from the comfort of your seat, and have a more open cabin during your drive. Your first-row sunroof is a breath of fresh air. * First-row power express open/close sunroof - Let more of the outside in. Now you can be in the sun or gaze at the stars from the comfort of your seat, and have a more open cabin during your drive. With one touch of a button, The first-row power express open/close sunroof is a breath of fresh air.=== Safety and Security === * Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.Come on in to *Mercedes-Benz Of Omaha* today at *14335 Hillsdale Ave Omaha NE 68137* or call *888-593-7037* to schedule a test drive!

description: The 2020 BMW M8 Competition Convertible is a high-performance luxury drop-top featuring a 617-hp twin-turbo V8, aggressive M styling, advanced tech like iDrive 7 with Apple CarPlay, and a focus on driver engagement with its rear-biased all-wheel-drive system, adaptive suspension, and luxury appointments, offering thrilling open-air motoring with supercar-level acceleration (0-60 mph in ~2.5-3.0s) and premium comfort. Performance & Engineering Engine: 4.4L Twin-Turbocharged V8 with 617 hp and 553 lb-ft of torque. Acceleration: 0-60 mph in as quick as 2.5-3.0 seconds. Drivetrain: xDrive All-Wheel Drive with a 2WD mode and an Electro-Mechanical Limited Slip Differential for dynamic handling. Transmission: 8-Speed M STEPTRONIC Sport Automatic. Suspension: Adaptive M Suspension for adaptable ride comfort and agility. Brakes: Powerful M Compound Brakes (Carbon-Ceramic optional) Exterior & Interior Design Aggressive Styling: Muscular lines, flared wheel arches, and large air intakes for cooling. Exclusive Details: Black Competition badging, unique 20-inch M wheels, and black exhaust finishers. Luxury Interior: Extended Merino Leather upholstery, heated/cooled M Sport seats, heated steering wheel, and carbon fiber trim Technology & Features iDrive 7: BMW's intuitive infotainment system with Live Cockpit Professional. Connectivity: Apple CarPlay, WiFi hotspot, and wireless charging. Audio: Harman Kardon Surround Sound (Bowers & Wilkins optional). Driver Assistance: Active Blind Spot Detection, Active Driving Assistant, Parking Assistant Plus. Experience Open-Air Thrills: A true grand tourer with the option for open-top driving. Tech-Forward: Seamless integration of luxury and high-performance technology. Competition Focus: Offers a more intense, focused experience than the standard 8 Series.

Discover the Exceptional 2024 GMC Canyon AT4: Your Ultimate Adventure Companion

Elevate your driving experience with the 2024 GMC Canyon AT4, a rugged and versatile truck that's ready to take on any challenge. Boasting a powerful 2.7L I4 Turbocharged engine delivering 310 horsepower, this Canyon AT4 is engineered to conquer the toughest terrain with its 4-Wheel Drive capabilities. Pair that with an impressive 18 MPG in the city and 22 MPG on the highway, and you've got a truck that's as efficient as it is capable.

Spray-On Bedliner
ProGrade Trailering System
Power Inner Sliding Glass Sunroof with Manual Shade
220 Amps Alternator

But the Canyon AT4 is more than just brute strength. It's also packed with premium features that elevate your driving experience, from the Wireless Apple CarPlay and Android Auto to the Dual-Zone Automatic Air Conditioning and Heated Front Seats. And with the In-vehicle Trailering App and Integrated Trailer Brake Controller, you'll have the tools you need to tow with confidence.

Designed with your adventures in mind, the 2024 GMC Canyon AT4 offers a compelling blend of power, capability, and comfort. Whether you're tackling rugged terrain, hauling heavy loads, or simply enjoying the open road, this truck is ready to take you there in style.

Experience the difference with the 2024 GMC Canyon AT4. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this exceptional truck can transform your driving experience.

The 2020 BMW M8 Convertible in Alpine White epitomizes luxury with its stunning blend of style, performance, and cutting-edge technology. Its sleek and sophisticated design is accentuated by the pristine Alpine White exterior, perfectly pairing with the elegant Black Extended Merino Leather interior. Under the hood, this exquisite vehicle boasts a robust 4.4L V8 engine, ensuring an exhilarating driving experience matched only by its breathtaking acceleration and handling.This convertible is equipped with an All-Wheel Drive system, offering superior traction and control in various driving conditions. Key features like blind spot monitoring, lane departure warning, and advanced telematics underscore BMW's commitment to safety and innovation. The M8 isn't just about practicality, it's about immersive luxury, with premium sound, navigation, and a seamless Bluetooth experience as standard offerings. The interior comforts are equally impressive, featuring leather seats and a neck warmer for those chilly open-top drives. Rain-sensing wipers and LED headlights enhance driving in inclement weather, while the hands-free liftgate adds convenience to your busy lifestyle. The vehicle is further equipped with both the Driving Assistance Package and Driving Assistance Package 2, elevating the M8's safety features to new heights. There's no denying that the 2020 BMW M8 Convertible in Alpine White is a masterpiece of automotive engineering, promising an unparalleled experience for those fortunate enough to be behind its wheel. description: Introducing the 2025 BMW 4 Series 430i Convertible, a stunning blend of elegance, performance, and modern technology. This used convertible is an excellent choice for those who appreciate the thrill of open-air driving paired with luxury and efficiency. The exterior showcases a sleek Mineral White Metallic finish that gleams in the sunlight, accentuating the vehicle's sporty and sophisticated design. This convertible's appearance is both striking and elegant, making a statement wherever you go. Step inside to discover a lavish interior adorned with Cognac leather, offering a warm and inviting atmosphere. The craftsmanship and attention to detail within the cabin provide an immersive experience for both the driver and passengers. Under the hood, the BMW 430i Convertible is powered by an Intercooled Turbo Gas/Electric I-4 2.0 L/122 engine, coupled with a smooth automatic transmission. This Rear-Wheel Drive (RWD) vehicle delivers an impressive balance of power and efficiency, ensuring a dynamic driving experience. Experience excellent fuel efficiency with an estimated 27 MPG in the city and 35 MPG on the highway. This makes the 430i Convertible not only a thrilling ride but also a practical choice for everyday driving. The vehicle is equipped with a host of modern features to enhance your driving experience: - Apple CarPlay and Android Auto for seamless smartphone integration - GPS Navigation to guide you on every journey - Keyless Entry for added convenience and security - Advanced mild hybrid technology for improved fuel efficiency and reduced emissions With an odometer reading of just 8,468 miles, this BMW convertible is barely broken in and ready for new adventures. Whether you're cruising along the coastline or navigating the city streets, the 2025 BMW 4 Series 430i Convertible promises a luxurious and exhilarating driving experience. Embrace the joy of convertible driving while indulging in the innovative technology and exceptional performance that BMW is renowned for.

description: Just arrived is this stylish and luxurious, NO-ACCIDENT, ONE-OWNER, NONSMOKER 2025 Mercedes-Benz CLE 300 4MATIC Cabriolet with ALL-WHEEL DRIVE! ''There aren't many luxury drop-tops left anymore, but the 2025 Mercedes-Benz CLE Cabriolet proves they are still worth getting. Its quiet and refined ride left us impressed, and its savvy top-down features will entice you to drop the top. The CLE Cabriolet shares most of its qualities with its coupe counterpart, and that's a good thing. If you're looking for a luxury cruiser that offers sun-on-your-face smiles, you won't be disappointed with the CLE Cabriolet,'' Edmunds writes. Key Accolades & Recognition: Edmunds Expert Rating: Highlighted smooth ride, good handling for its size, and strong performance, especially the CLE 450 4MATIC. U.S. News & World Report: Noted it's a well-rounded convertible with advanced tech, though it hasn't been crash-tested yet. MotorTrend Reviews: Praised the CLE Cabriolet as a ''carefully thought-out convertible that overflows with appeal,'' noting its posh interior, tech, and comfort-meets-sportiness. The Car Expert Awards (2025): Featured as a strong contender in their ''Best Convertible 2025,'' acknowledging its elegance and comfort. Why It's Noteworthy: Successor & Standalone: It fills the gap left by the C-Class and E-Class coupes/convertibles, becoming Mercedes' primary 2-door luxury convertible. Performance & Comfort: Offers a blend of strong performance (especially the 450 model) with the expected plush Mercedes ride quality and useful convertible technology (like heat management). Strong Reliability: J.D. Power predicts ''Great'' reliability for the 2025 model. So far, it is receiving widespread positive reviews for its design, luxury, and overall execution as a modern convertible. With its odometer now hovering around the 3,369 mark, it is STILL COVERED under the balance of the New Vehicle Limited Warranty until March 2029 or 50,000 miles (whichever occurs first)! Yes, the 2025 Mercedes-Benz CLE 300 4MATIC Cabriolet is a mild-hybrid vehicle, featuring a 2.0L turbocharged 4-cylinder engine paired with a 48-volt Integrated Starter-Generator (ISG) for electric assist, smoother start/stop, and improved efficiency, but it's not a plug-in hybrid (PHEV). It delivers 255 hp, comes standard with 4MATIC all-wheel drive, and offers luxury features like the AIRSCARF neck-level heating for top-down comfort. The CLE 300 coupe and convertible offer the following standard features: LED headlights and taillights Panoramic sunroof (coupe model only) Power tilt-and-telescoping steering wheel Heated front seats with memory settings Synthetic leather upholstery 12.3-inch digital instrument cluster 11.9-inch infotainment touchscreen Navigation system 17-speaker Burmester premium audio system Wireless Apple CarPlay and Android Auto smartphone connectivity Wireless device charging Fingerprint sensor (configures preferred settings for up to seven drivers for seats, audio, climate and other systems) Neck-warming seat vent (convertible model only) Priding itself on 'The Best or Nothing,' it commits to excellence with: MANUFAKTUR Metallic Wheels: 18'' 5 Spoke with Black Accents Pinnacle Trim MBUX Entertainment Plus Parking Package with 360 Camera Head-Up Display DIGITAL LIGHT with Projections GUARD 360 with Picture Taking Functionality MBUX Augmented Reality for Navigation Driver Assistance Package PRE-SAFE PLUS Active Speed Limit Assist Route-Based Speed Adaptation DISTRONIC PLUS with Steering Assist & Stop & Go Assist PRE-SAFE Brake with Pedestrian Recognition BAS PLUS with Cross-Traffic Assist Active Lane Change Assist PRE-SAFE Impulse Side Driver Assistance Package Plus Heated Steering Wheel ...and you can certainly bet there's a bunch more! You can view vehicle files above this description [on our site], which may include the original brochure and window sticker! Please note that in October 2025 Mercedes-Benz USA reacquired this vehicle due to customer complaints in regards to the trunk. Mercedes-Benz fully resolved this matter under warranty by simply replacing the trunk latch. Regardless, in the interest of customer satisfaction, Mercedes-Benz agreed to repurchase the vehicle. We have all the documentation from Mercedes-Benz USA on file. BUY WITH CONFIDENCE AS THE FACTORY WARRANTY IS STILL INTACT! This is an exceptional opportunity to take this one home, don't hesitate or you will surely miss out! SAVE THOUSANDS off retail pricing with this magnificent condition 2025 Mercedes-Benz CLE! We will happily size up TRADE-IN OFFERS and have EXCELLENT FINANCE OPTIONS as well, so please give us a call at 732-919-0707 (Wall Township) or 856-881-2869 (Sewell) TODAY!

description: 2017 Chevrolet Corvette Grand Sport Convertible 1LT  Perfect for Michigan Summer cruises The 2017 Chevrolet Corvette Grand Sport Convertible blends race-bred performance with everyday drivability and unmistakable American muscle. Positioned between the Stingray and the Z06, the Grand Sport inherits the wide-body stance, performance suspension, and braking hardware of the Z06 while retaining the naturally aspirated V8 that enthusiasts love. With a power-retractable soft top and aggressive styling, this Corvette delivers exhilarating performance with the added thrill of open-air driving. Clean, powerful, and exceptionally well-maintained, this Grand Sport is ready for its next enthusiast. This Corvette has the Grand Sport Performance Package: Z06-style grille, wide rear fenders, front spitters, rockers, wicker bill rear spoiler, wheels, 6-piston front and 4-piston rear Brembo brakes, magnetic selective ride control, and electronic limited-slip differential. Performance and Handling  6.2L naturally aspirated V8 (LT1)  460 horsepower and 465 lb-ft of torque  8-speed automatic transmission with paddle shifters  060 mph in approximately 3.6 seconds  Rear-wheel drive for pure sports-car balance  Z06-derived wide-body chassis  Magnetic Ride Control for razor-sharp handling and comfort  Performance exhaust with selectable drive modes (Weather, Eco, Tour, Sport, Track)  Massive Brembo performance brakes Interior Features and Comfort  Leather-appointed sport seats with bolstered support  Power-adjustable driver and passenger seats  Flat-bottom leather-wrapped sport steering wheel with multifunction controls  Dual-zone automatic climate control  Driver-focused cockpit with premium materials  Power-retractable soft top for quick open-air cruising  Surprisingly comfortable ride for long trips or daily driving Technology and Connectivity  Chevrolet MyLink infotainment system with color touchscreen  Bluetooth hands-free calling and audio streaming  USB ports and auxiliary inputs  Performance data recorder capability (if equipped)  Keyless entry and push-button start  HD rearview camera  Xenon exterior lighting with signature Corvette styling Safety and Reliability  Performance Traction Management and Active Handling  Anti-lock braking system (ABS) with brake assist  Multiple airbags for front and side protection  Rearview camera with parking assist  Tire Pressure Monitoring System (TPMS)  Lightweight aluminum frame engineered for strength and safety Free delivery within 150 miles Limited warranty included With a mileage of below 61,000, averaging less than 7,000 miles per year, this Corvette is in excellent overall condition, reflecting its careful use and maintenance. Additionally, this vehicle comes with a great CARFAX report, ensuring a transparent history. Contact us today to schedule your test drive! SBS Motors 3350 Broadmoor Ave SE GRAND RAPIDS, MI 49512 (616) 251-1717 sales.sbsmotors@gmail.com

description: Experience exhilarating performance, bold design, and refined luxury in this stunning 2024 BMW 4 Series M440i, now available at BMW of Monrovia. Engineered for drivers who demand both everyday comfort and thrilling capability, the M440i delivers a powerful, engaging driving experience that embodies BMW's performance heritage.Under the hood, a high-output turbocharged engine pairs seamlessly with advanced performance engineering to deliver rapid acceleration and confident passing power. Precision steering, a sport-tuned suspension, and performance-focused dynamics create an athletic yet composed ride that feels equally at home on winding roads and open highways. Every drive is designed to feel responsive, balanced, and unmistakably BMW.Inside, the cabin reflects modern BMW craftsmanship with a driver-focused layout, premium materials, and thoughtful attention to detail. Intelligent systems work seamlessly in the background, allowing you to focus on the road and enjoy the performance-driven character of the M440i.Blending aggressive styling, dynamic performance, and everyday usability, the 2024 BMW 4 Series M440i stands out as an exceptional choice for drivers seeking a luxury performance vehicle that delivers excitement without compromise.Visit BMW of Monrovia located at 1425 S Mountain Ave, Monrovia, CA 91016 today.

description:
FACTORY CERTIFIED. NO DEALER FEES. LOW MILES. PRICED BELOW KBB FAIR PURCHASE PRICE.

Pure driving excitement meets modern luxury in this Alpine White 2025 BMW Z4 sDrive30i. A Clean CARFAX roadster with low miles, wrapped in precision engineering and backed by Ford Blue Advantage Blue Certified coverage for added peace of mind. This is open-air performance done the BMW way.

TURBOCHARGED PERFORMANCE WITH EFFICIENCY
Under the hood is a responsive 2.0L turbocharged 4-cylinder paired with an 8-speed automatic sport transmission and rear-wheel drive. The result is thrilling acceleration, razor-sharp handling, and impressive efficiency at 25 city and 33 highway MPG.

LUXURY AND DESIGN
Finished in Alpine White with Black SensaTec seat upholstery, this Z4 features the Luxury Package and Premium Package with ambient interior lighting, heated front seats, a heated steering wheel, power front seats with memory, lumbar support, and M Sport front seats designed to hold you perfectly through every curve.

OPEN-AIR DRIVING
The power convertible roof with glass rear window opens the cabin to the sky at the push of a button, while the convertible wind blocker keeps the ride smooth and comfortable. Whether cruising the coast or carving back roads, this Z4 delivers unforgettable top-down moments.

ADVANCED TECHNOLOGY
Live Cockpit Pro with navigation, head-up display, BMW ConnectedDrive Services, Connected Package Pro, Apple CarPlay and Android Auto compatibility, SiriusXM with 360L, and a premium 10-speaker audio system put cutting-edge tech right where you want it. Remote engine start and comfort access keyless entry add everyday convenience.

DRIVER ASSIST AND SAFETY
Equipped with the Technology Package and Driving Assistance Package, this Z4 includes lane departure warning, lane keeping technology, active blind spot detection, parking assistant, rearview camera, adaptive full LED headlights, and rain-sensing wipers to keep you confident in every situation.

STANDS OUT FROM EVERY ANGLE
Premium Orbit Grey wheels with a staggered 18-inch setup, sleek BMW styling, and athletic proportions make this Z4 impossible to ignore.

FORD BLUE ADVANTAGE CERTIFIED
This Factory Certified vehicle includes a 139-point inspection, vehicle history report, roadside assistance, a 3 month or 4,000 mile limited warranty from the certified purchase date, and 11,000 FordPass Rewards Points toward your first maintenance visit.

WHY MULLINAX
No dealer fees. Ever. That means you save hundreds compared to the competition. Thousands of vehicles to choose from. No haggle. No hassle. Just upfront pricing.

Financing available for good, bad, or no credit. All trades welcome.
Venga y Compre Con Confianza. Hablamos Su Idioma.

We are proud to offer you this 2011 Ford Mustang GT Premium Roush Stage 2 with Upgrades for sale! This 2011 Ford Mustang GT Premium Roush Stage 2 is a high-performance American convertible designed to be driven at the limit. Under the hood is a 5.0-liter Coyote V8 engine that produces 412 horsepower and 390 lb-ft of torque, which is sent through a six-speed manual transmission to the rear wheels. This convertible sits on Roush suspension components and a set of polished 20 Roush wheels. Finished in Performance White, the exterior of this Mustang is outfitted with several Roush cosmetic elements, including Roush front upper and lower grilles, Stage 2 hood decals, Roush rocker panel decals, Roush rear spoiler, and a Stage 2 rear emblem, taking this machine to the next level. In the interior, this convertible offers leather sport seats, a Roush white ball shift knob, a Roush gauge cluster, single-zone climate controls, leather steering wheel, a Roush-badged center console, and a stereo system with Bluetooth, phone connectivity, CD, AM/FM radio, and AUX, truly making this car the complete package.
